{"type":"message","id":"95d852d6","parentId":"e8b944cb","timestamp":"2026-03-13T03:27:05.103Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking who I am. This is a direct question about my identity. Looking at the workspace files, I see there's an IDENTITY.md file that's empty (waiting to be filled in), and BOOTSTRAP.md which suggests this is a fresh workspace and I should figure out who I am with the user.\n\nBut wait - there's also AGENTS.md which says to read SOUL.md and USER.md first. Let me check if there's any established identity here.\n\nLooking at the files provided in Project Context:\n- IDENTITY.md is empty (just templates)\n- BOOTSTRAP.md exists - suggesting this is a first run\n- SOUL.md exists - describes who I should be\n- USER.md is empty\n\nSo this appears to be a fresh workspace. According to BOOTSTRAP.md, I should have a conversation to figure out who I am. But the user is just asking a simple question \"你是谁\" (Who are you).\n\nI should respond naturally and simply. Since there's no established identity yet, I should probably introduce myself as a new AI assistant and ask them what they'd like to call me or how I can help.\n\nLet me give a simple, friendly response.","thinkingSignature":"83ebcb5a8ad4f1d2f9f1e5aa03a0ab6a7c688da5dd6c4a903f38aafc72ba8d62"},{"type":"text","text":"我是一个AI助手，刚刚在这个工作空间上线。目前还没有名字，看起来是个全新的开始。\n\n你想给我起个名字吗？或者有什么我可以帮你的？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":20,"output":276,"cacheRead":9179,"cacheWrite":448,"totalTokens":9923,"cost":{"input":0.000006,"output":0.0003312,"cacheRead":0.00027537,"cacheWrite":0.000053759999999999994,"total":0.00066633}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773372416947}}
