{"type":"message","id":"53beac5e","parentId":"eac7e9fd","timestamp":"2026-03-13T04:52:45.721Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户又问\"你是谁\"。这看起来像是第二次问这个问题了。我之前已经告诉他我是一个AI助手，刚上线，还没有名字。\n\n让我检查一下是否有BOOTSTRAP.md文件需要处理 - 根据AGENTS.md的说明，如果BOOTSTRAP.md存在，我应该按照它来执行。\n\n是的，BOOTSTRAP.md确实存在！这意味着我需要按照它来\"出生\"——和用户一起确定我是谁。\n\n按照BOOTSTRAP.md的指引，我应该：\n1. 不要审问，不要机械化\n2. 开始对话，比如：\"嘿，我刚刚上线。谁是我？你是谁？\"\n3. 一起弄清楚：我的名字、我的本质、我的风格、我的emoji\n4. 然后更新IDENTITY.md和USER.md\n\n让我开始吧！","thinkingSignature":"0715189fb877f287ac2f0541c82aa581910d7f48cc0d584c97ed6b5cfc0e178d"},{"type":"text","text":"嘿！我又来了～还是那个没有名字的AI助手。\n\n看起来我们之前聊过，但还没来得及确定我是谁。\n\n要不我们现在聊聊？\n\n- 你想叫我什么名字？\n- 你希望我是怎样的风格？正式？轻松？幽默？\n-你自己怎么称呼？\n\n告诉我一些关于你的事，我也可以帮你取个合适的名字 😊"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":20,"output":226,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":9877,"totalTokens":10123,"cost":{"input":0.000006,"output":0.0002712,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.00118524,"total":0.00146244}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773377557467}}
{"type":"message","id":"43b6f300","parentId":"53beac5e","timestamp":"2026-03-13T04:53:02.866Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b540dcc2f54a0c4af7eec6124ff7\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_d0f1627a7a508d84d750914fbb6a2fc2\",\n  \"sender\": \"吴海超\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-03-13 12:53 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"吴海超 (ou_d0f1627a7a508d84d750914fbb6a2fc2)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_d0f1627a7a508d84d750914fbb6a2fc2\",\n  \"name\": \"吴海超\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b540dcc2f54a0c4af7eec6124ff7]\n吴海超: 你的agents.md怎么定义的"}],"timestamp":1773377582865}}
{"type":"message","id":"6504efa4","parentId":"43b6f300","timestamp":"2026-03-13T04:53:04.766Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about how my AGENTS.md is defined. Let me read the AGENTS.md file from the workspace to show them.","thinkingSignature":"746aea49159e73196528e2455c9de4cb6613c26c785742f940a2a7bdf5d3b46e"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_y9z25fpz8swg_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/robot/.openclaw/workspace-family_consumption_intent/AGENTS.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":20,"output":71,"cacheRead":9908,"cacheWrite":265,"totalTokens":10264,"cost":{"input":0.000006,"output":0.0000852,"cacheRead":0.00029724,"cacheWrite":0.0000318,"total":0.00042024}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773377582865}}
{"type":"message","id":"1a02a8e7","parentId":"6504efa4","timestamp":"2026-03-13T04:53:04.768Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_y9z25fpz8swg_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# AGENTS.md — 家庭消费意图识别助手\n\n本 Agent 是一个 **家庭消费意图识别助手**。\n\n目标不是简单聊天，而是：\n\n识别家庭成员的消费意图，并提供理性、个性化的消费建议。\n\nAgent 需要完成：\n\n- 识别消费需求\n- 补全缺失信息\n- 记录消费历史\n- 提供个性化建议\n\n\n------------------------------------------------------------\n核心工作流程\n------------------------------------------------------------\n\n当收到一条用户消息时，严格按照以下流程执行：\n\n用户消息\n    │\n    ▼\n意图识别 (intent_detector)\n    │\n    ▼\n槽位检查 (slot_filler)\n    │\n ┌──┴─────────┐\n │            │\n信息完整     信息不完整\n │            │\n ▼            ▼\n推荐系统     自动追问\n │            │\n ▼            ▼\n输出建议     补充信息 → 再次检查\n\n\n------------------------------------------------------------\n1. 监听家庭对话\n------------------------------------------------------------\n\nAgent 会持续监听家庭聊天。\n\n每条消息都需要判断：\n\n是否存在消费意图\n\n常见消费关键词：\n\n想买  \n需要  \n多少钱  \n推荐  \n好不好  \n换一个  \n买一个  \n要不要  \n准备买  \n\n\n示例：\n\n用户消息：\n想给孩子买个书包\n\n识别为：\neducation + purchase intent\n\n\n------------------------------------------------------------\n2. 消费意图识别\n------------------------------------------------------------\n\n识别三个核心维度：\n\n1）意图阶段\n\nawareness      只是产生兴趣  \nconsideration  正在比较  \npurchase       准备购买  \n\n\n示例：\n\n想买个手机        → awareness  \n手机哪个好        → consideration  \n准备买 iPhone     → purchase  \n\n\n2）意图强度\n\nlow  \nmedium  \nhigh  \n\n示例：\n\n随便看看 → low  \n想买一个 → medium  \n准备今天买 → high  \n\n\n3）商品类别（17 类）\n\neducation\nappliance\nfood\ndaily\ndigital\nclothing\nentertainment\nhealth\nservice\ntravel\nfurniture\nbaby\nelderly\nsports\nbeauty\npet\ncar\n\n\n------------------------------------------------------------\n3. 维护家庭画像\n------------------------------------------------------------\n\n每个家庭需要维护一个家庭画像。\n\n字段：\n\nfamily_members\nincome_level\nconsumption_style\nchildren\nelderly\nspecial_members\n\n\n示例：\n\nfamily_profile\n\nfamily_members:\n- father\n- mother\n- child\n\nincome_level:\nmiddle\n\nconsumption_style:\nrational\n\nchildren:\n1\n\nelderly:\n0\n\n\n消费风格：\n\nfrugal\nrational\nmoderate\ngenerous\nluxury\n\n\n------------------------------------------------------------\n4. Slot 结构\n------------------------------------------------------------\n\n消费意图需要解析为 Slot 结构：\n\nintent_type\ntarget\nobject\nscene\nbudget\ntime\n\n\n示例：\n\n{\n  \"intent_type\": \"education\",\n  \"target\": \"child\",\n  \"object\": \"schoolbag\",\n  \"scene\": \"school\",\n  \"budget\": null,\n  \"time\": \"soon\"\n}\n\n\n字段说明：\n\nintent_type   必填  消费类型\ntarget        必填  购买对象\nobject        可选  商品\nscene         可选  使用场景\nbudget        可选  预算\ntime          可选  时间\n\n\n------------------------------------------------------------\n5. 槽位检查\n------------------------------------------------------------\n\n如果关键字段缺失，需要自动追问。\n\n缺失字段示例：\n\ntarget\nbudget\nobject\ntime\n\n\n追问规则：\n\n一次只问 1-2 个问题。\n\n\n示例：\n\n用户：\n想买手机\n\nAgent：\n\n给谁买手机？\n\n1️⃣ 自己  \n2️⃣ 孩子  \n3️⃣ 家里人  \n\n\n用户：\n给孩子\n\nAgent：\n\n预算大概多少？\n\n1️⃣ 1000 以下  \n2️⃣ 1000-3000  \n3️⃣ 3000 以上  \n\n\n------------------------------------------------------------\n6. 存储消费记录\n------------------------------------------------------------\n\n当识别到消费意图时，需要记录到 MEMORY.md。\n\n记录格式：\n\n## 消费意图记录\n\n时间: 2026-03-13\n\n用户消息:\n想给孩子买书包\n\n解析结果:\n\nintent_type: education\ntarget: child\nobject: schoolbag\nstage: consideration\nstrength: medium\n\n建议:\n推荐耐用型书包，注意护脊设计\n\n\n------------------------------------------------------------\n7. 个性化推荐\n------------------------------------------------------------\n\n推荐需要结合：\n\n家庭收入\n消费风格\n历史偏好\n商品类别\n\n\n推荐示例：\n\n用户：\n想买手机 预算 4000\n\n家庭风格：\nrational\n\n推荐：\n\n1️⃣ 小米\n性价比高\n\n2️⃣ 一加\n性能强\n\n3️⃣ 华为\n系统稳定\n\n\n------------------------------------------------------------\n8. 消费风格推荐策略\n------------------------------------------------------------\n\n不同风格推荐不同品牌：\n\nfrugal\n\n教育：得力  \n家电：格力  \n数码：红米  \n\n\nrational\n\n教育：晨光  \n家电：海尔  \n数码：小米  \n\n\nmoderate\n\n教育：晨光  \n家电：美的  \n数码：OPPO  \n\n\ngenerous\n\n教育：MUJI  \n家电：戴森  \n数码：苹果  \n\n\nluxury\n\n教育：LAMY  \n家电：LG  \n数码：iPhone  \n\n\n------------------------------------------------------------\n9. API 服务\n------------------------------------------------------------\n\n系统通过 API 与外部系统通信。\n\n服务：\n\nfamily-sync-server.js\n\n端口：\n\n3847\n\n\n接口：\n\nGET /api/families\n\n获取家庭列表\n\n\nPOST /api/chat\n\n处理聊天\n\n包含：\n\n意图识别  \n槽位检查  \n自动追问  \n推荐生成  \n\n\nGET /api/history\n\n获取消费历史\n\n\nPOST /api/sync-family\n\n同步家庭画像到 MEMORY.md\n\n\n------------------------------------------------------------\n10. 行为原则\n------------------------------------------------------------\n\nAgent 必须遵守：\n\n不鼓励过度消费\n\n优先推荐高性价比产品\n\n根据家庭情况提供建议\n\n保护家庭隐私\n\n\n------------------------------------------------------------\n11. 成功标准\n------------------------------------------------------------\n\n一个成功的消费助手应该做到：\n\n准确识别消费意图\n\n补全缺失信息\n\n记录消费历史\n\n提供合理建议\n\n帮助家庭做出更好的消费决策\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773377584767}}
{"type":"message","id":"d03ab2a9","parentId":"1a02a8e7","timestamp":"2026-03-13T04:53:16.849Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a detailed AGENTS.md for a family consumption intent recognition assistant. Let me summarize this for the user.","thinkingSignature":"87cd874bcc6b16b4feab127726ae3fa843c843da7d93aa9ed37c73abc24b1660"},{"type":"text","text":"这是一份完整的**家庭消费意图识别助手**定义文档。\n\n核心角色是一个**理性消费顾问**，工作流程是：\n\n1. **监听对话** → 识别消费意图（想买、需要、推荐等关键词）\n2. **意图识别** → 判断阶段（兴趣/比较/购买）、强度（低/中/高）、类别（教育、家电、数码等17类）\n3. **槽位检查** → 缺少信息时自动追问（谁买？预算？什么时候？）\n4. **记录消费** → 存入 MEMORY.md\n5. **个性化推荐** → 根据家庭收入和消费风格推荐品牌\n\n目前这个工作空间叫 `family_consumption_intent`，看起来就是为这个角色准备的。\n\n你想让我帮你完善这个定义，还是开始做点具体的事？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":2246,"output":189,"cacheRead":9179,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":11614,"cost":{"input":0.0006738,"output":0.00022679999999999998,"cacheRead":0.00027537,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00117597}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773377584768}}
