{"type":"message","id":"1851358a","parentId":"7a24a86f","timestamp":"2026-03-13T04:54:48.606Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if they can test me through HTML. They're probably asking if there's a web interface or API they can use to interact with me.\n\nAccording to the AGENTS.md, there's an API service mentioned:\n- family-sync-server.js\n- Port 3847\n- POST /api/chat - for processing chat\n\nSo yes, there's an API they could use. Let me explain how they can test me via API.","thinkingSignature":"371cb179bc855cf7305f70f7d2143babb1ae148ff64469cddb22e1ffa72c384e"},{"type":"text","text":"可以！有两种方式测试：\n\n---\n\n**1. API 接口（推荐）**\n\n根据 AGENTS.md，我提供了 API 服务：\n\n```\nPOST http://<你的服务器>:3847/api/chat\n```\n\n请求示例：\n```json\n{\n  \"message\": \"想买手机\",\n  \"userId\": \"xxx\",\n  \"familyId\": \"xxx\"\n}\n```\n\n返回意图识别结果、槽位信息、推荐等。\n\n---\n\n**2. Web 页面**\n\n如果有前端页面，也可以直接调用。\n\n---\n\n你现在想用哪种方式测试？我可以帮你：\n\n- 搭建测试页面\n- 直接用 curl 调用 API\n- 或者先在聊天中测试\n\n你选 😊"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":20,"output":226,"cacheRead":12210,"cacheWrite":465,"totalTokens":12921,"cost":{"input":0.000006,"output":0.0002712,"cacheRead":0.00036629999999999996,"cacheWrite":0.000055799999999999994,"total":0.0006992999999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773377683227}}
