{"type":"message","id":"e179704c","parentId":"45027f1d","timestamp":"2026-03-13T05:00:11.489Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see the image - it's a Feishu (飞书) chatbot test page. It has:\n- A clean, modern design with a light gray/white background\n- A chat-like interface with:\n  - A header \"消费意图识别助手 - V1.0.0\"\n  - A \"新建对话\" button\n  - Chat messages with user on the right (blue bubble) and bot on the left (gray bubble)\n  - Input area at the bottom with a send button\n  - Intent recognition results showing: 意图类型: 礼物, 购买阶段: awareness, 购买强度: low\n  - A thinking indicator \"思考中...\"\n\nThis is a chat-style interface. I need to redesign the test.html to match this style - chat bubbles, clean design, intent recognition display.","thinkingSignature":"1563ab3632a38b06cd5aa2cd33704c7f544c3d97eb2d6590d9e3789bd003eaeb"},{"type":"text","text":"明白了！这是个聊天风格的测试页面。我来重新设计：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_v5lq9w8mtpsq_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n  <title>消费意图识别助手 - V1.0.0</title>\n  <style>\n    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }\n    body {\n      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'PingFang SC', sans-serif;\n      background: #f5f5f5;\n      height: 100vh;\n      display: flex;\n      flex-direction: column;\n    }\n    \n    /* 顶部导航 */\n    .header {\n      background: #fff;\n      padding: 12px 20px;\n      display: flex;\n      justify-content: space-between;\n      align-items: center;\n      border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e5e5;\n    }\n    .header h1 {\n      font-size: 16px;\n      color: #333;\n      font-weight: 500;\n    }\n    .new-chat-btn {\n      background: #4A90E2;\n      color: white;\n      border: none;\n      padding: 6px 16px;\n      border-radius: 4px;\n      cursor: pointer;\n      font-size: 13px;\n    }\n    .new-chat-btn:hover { background: #357ABD; }\n    \n    /* 聊天区域 */\n    .chat-container {\n      flex: 1;\n      overflow-y: auto;\n      padding: 20px;\n      max-width: 800px;\n      margin: 0 auto;\n      width: 100%;\n    }\n    \n    .message {\n      display: flex;\n      margin-bottom: 20px;\n      align-items: flex-start;\n    }\n    .message.user {\n      flex-direction: row-reverse;\n    }\n    .message.bot {\n      flex-direction: row;\n    }\n    \n    .avatar {\n      width: 36px;\n      height: 36px;\n      border-radius: 50%;\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      justify-content: center;\n      font-size: 18px;\n      flex-shrink: 0;\n    }\n    .user .avatar {\n      background: #4A90E2;\n      color: white;\n      margin-left: 10px;\n    }\n    .bot .avatar {\n      background: #e5e5e5;\n      color: #666;\n      margin-right: 10px;\n    }\n    \n    .bubble {\n      max-width: 70%;\n      padding: 10px 14px;\n      border-radius: 8px;\n      font-size: 14px;\n      line-height: 1.5;\n      word-wrap: break-word;\n    }\n    .user .bubble {\n      background: #4A90E2;\n      color: white;\n      border-top-right-radius: 4px;\n    }\n    .bot .bubble {\n      background: #fff;\n      color: #333;\n      border: 1px solid #e5e5e5;\n      border-top-left-radius: 4px;\n    }\n    \n    /* 意图识别结果 */\n    .intent-result {\n      background: #f8f9fa;\n      border-radius: 8px;\n      padding: 12px;\n      margin-top: 8px;\n      font-size: 13px;\n    }\n    .intent-result .title {\n      font-weight: 500;\n      color: #666;\n      margin-bottom: 8px;\n    }\n    .intent-tags {\n      display: flex;\n      flex-wrap: wrap;\n      gap: 6px;\n    }\n    .intent-tag {\n      background: #e8f4fd;\n      color: #4A90E2;\n      padding: 3px 10px;\n      border-radius: 4px;\n      font-size: 12px;\n    }\n    .intent-tag strong { font-weight: 500; }\n    \n    /* 追问气泡 */\n    .question-bubble {\n      margin-top: 8px;\n    }\n    .question-options {\n      display: flex;\n      flex-wrap: wrap;\n      gap: 8px;\n      margin-top: 8px;\n    }\n    .option-btn {\n      background: #f0f7ff;\n      color: #4A90E2;\n      border: 1px solid #4A90E2;\n      padding: 6px 14px;\n      border-radius: 16px;\n      cursor: pointer;\n      font-size: 13px;\n    }\n    .option-btn:hover {\n      background: #4A90E2;\n      color: white;\n    }\n    \n    /* 输入区域 */\n    .input-area {\n      background: #fff;\n      padding: 16px 20px;\n      border-top: 1px solid #e5e5e5;\n    }\n    .input-wrapper {\n      max-width: 800px;\n      margin: 0 auto;\n      display: flex;\n      gap: 10px;\n    }\n    .input-wrapper input {\n      flex: 1;\n      padding: 10px 14px;\n      border: 1px solid #e5e5e5;\n      border-radius: 20px;\n      font-size: 14px;\n      outline: none;\n    }\n    .input-wrapper input:focus {\n      border-color: #4A90E2;\n    }\n    .input-wrapper button {\n      background: #4A90E2;\n      color: white;\n      border: none;\n      padding: 10px 20px;\n      border-radius: 20px;\n      cursor: pointer;\n      font-size: 14px;\n    }\n    .input-wrapper button:hover {\n      background: #357ABD;\n    }\n    .input-wrapper button:disabled {\n      background: #ccc;\n    }\n    \n    /* 思考中 */\n    .thinking {\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      gap: 8px;\n      color: #999;\n      font-size: 13px;\n      padding: 10px 14px;\n    }\n    .thinking-dots {\n      display: flex;\n      gap: 4px;\n    }\n    .thinking-dots span {\n      width: 6px;\n      height: 6px;\n      background: #999;\n      border-radius: 50%;\n      animation: bounce 1.4s infinite ease-in-out;\n    }\n    .thinking-dots span:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: -0.32s; }\n    .thinking-dots span:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: -0.16s; }\n    @keyframes bounce {\n      0%, 80%, 100% { transform: scale(0); }\n      40% { transform: scale(1); }\n    }\n    \n    /* 空状态 */\n    .empty-state {\n      text-align: center;\n      padding: 60px 20px;\n      color: #999;\n    }\n    .empty-state .icon {\n      font-size: 48px;\n      margin-bottom: 16px;\n    }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <div class=\"header\">\n    <h1>🏠 消费意图识别助手 - V1.0.0</h1>\n    <button class=\"new-chat-btn\" onclick=\"newChat()\">新建对话</button>\n  </div>\n  \n  <div class=\"chat-container\" id=\"chatContainer\">\n    <div class=\"empty-state\" id=\"emptyState\">\n      <div class=\"icon\">💬</div>\n      <p>开始一个新对话吧</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  \n  <div class=\"input-area\">\n    <div class=\"input-wrapper\">\n      <input type=\"text\" id=\"messageInput\" placeholder=\"请输入消息...\" onkeypress=\"handleKeyPress(event)\">\n      <button onclick=\"sendMessage()\" id=\"sendBtn\">发送</button>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <script>\n    const API_URL = 'http://192.168.3.33:3847/api/chat';\n    let chatHistory = [];\n    \n    function handleKeyPress(e) {\n      if (e.key === 'Enter') sendMessage();\n    }\n    \n    function newChat() {\n      chatHistory = [];\n      renderChat();\n      document.getElementById('messageInput').focus();\n    }\n    \n    function renderChat() {\n      const container = document.getElementById('chatContainer');\n      const emptyState = document.getElementById('emptyState');\n      \n      if (chatHistory.length === 0) {\n        emptyState.style.display = 'block';\n        container.innerHTML = '';\n        container.appendChild(emptyState);\n        return;\n      }\n      \n      emptyState.style.display = 'none';\n      container.innerHTML = chatHistory.map(item => {\n        let html = '';\n        \n        // 用户消息\n        html += `<div class=\"message user\">\n          <div class=\"avatar\">🙂</div>\n          <div class=\"bubble\">${item.userMsg}</div>\n        </div>`;\n        \n        // Bot 回复\n        html += `<div class=\"message bot\">\n          <div class=\"avatar\">🤖</div>\n          <div class=\"bubble\">`;\n        \n        if (item.botReply) {\n          html += item.botReply;\n        }\n        \n        // 意图识别结果\n        if (item.intent) {\n          html += `<div class=\"intent-result\">\n            <div class=\"title\">🎯 意图识别结果</div>\n            <div class=\"intent-tags\">\n              <span class=\"intent-tag\"><strong>类型:</strong> ${item.intent.type || '-'}</span>\n              <span class=\"intent-tag\"><strong>阶段:</strong> ${item.intent.stage || '-'}</span>\n              <span class=\"intent-tag\"><strong>强度:</strong> ${item.intent.strength || '-'}</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>`;\n        }\n        \n        // 槽位信息\n        if (item.slots && Object.keys(item.slots).length > 0) {\n          html += `<div class=\"intent-result\" style=\"margin-top:8px;\">\n            <div class=\"title\">📋 槽位信息</div>\n            <div class=\"intent-tags\">\n              ${item.slots.target ? `<span class=\"intent-tag\"><strong>目标:</strong> ${item.slots.target}</span>` : ''}\n              ${item.slots.object ? `<span class=\"intent-tag\"><strong>商品:</strong> ${item.slots.object}</span>` : ''}\n              ${item.slots.budget ? `<span class=\"intent-tag\"><strong>预算:</strong> ${item.slots.budget}</span>` : ''}\n              ${item.slots.time ? `<span class=\"intent-tag\"><strong>时间:</strong> ${item.slots.time}</span>` : ''}\n              ${item.slots.scene ? `<span class=\"intent-tag\"><strong>场景:</strong> ${item.slots.scene}</span>` : ''}\n            </div>\n          </div>`;\n        }\n        \n        // 推荐\n        if (item.recommendations && item.recommendations.length > 0) {\n          html += `<div class=\"intent-result\" style=\"margin-top:8px;\">\n            <div class=\"title\">💡 推荐</div>\n            <div style=\"margin-top:6px;\">\n              ${item.recommendations.map(r => `<div>• <strong>${r.name}</strong>: ${r.reason || ''}</div>`).join('')}\n            </div>\n          </div>`;\n        }\n        \n        // 追问选项\n        if (item.options && item.options.length > 0) {\n          html += `<div class=\"question-bubble\">\n            <div class=\"question-options\">\n              ${item.options.map(opt => `<button class=\"option-btn\" onclick=\"selectOption('${opt}')\">${opt}</button>`).join('')}\n            </div>\n          </div>`;\n        }\n        \n        html += `</div></div>`;\n        \n        return html;\n      }).join('');\n      \n      // 滚动到底部\n      container.scrollTop = container.scrollHeight;\n    }\n    \n    function selectOption(option) {\n      const input = document.getElementById('messageInput');\n      input.value = option;\n      sendMessage();\n    }\n    \n    async function sendMessage() {\n      const input = document.getElementById('messageInput');\n      const message = input.value.trim();\n      if (!message) return;\n      \n      const sendBtn = document.getElementById('sendBtn');\n      sendBtn.disabled = true;\n      \n      // 添加用户消息\n      chatHistory.push({ userMsg: message, botReply: '思考中...', thinking: true });\n      renderChat();\n      \n      input.value = '';\n      \n      try {\n        const response = await fetch(API_URL, {\n          method: 'POST',\n          headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },\n          body: JSON.stringify({\n            message,\n            userId: 'test_user',\n            familyId: 'test_family'\n          })\n        });\n        \n        const data = await response.json();\n        \n        // 更新最后一条消息\n        chatHistory.pop();\n        chatHistory.push({\n          userMsg: message,\n          botReply: data.reply || '收到消息',\n          intent: data.intent,\n          slots: data.slots,\n          recommendations: data.recommendations,\n          options: data.options\n        });\n        \n        renderChat();\n      } catch (error) {\n        chatHistory.pop();\n        chatHistory.push({\n          userMsg: message,\n          botReply: `错误: ${error.message}`,\n          intent: null,\n          slots: {},\n          recommendations: [],\n          options: []\n        });\n        renderChat();\n      } finally {\n        sendBtn.disabled = false;\n        input.focus();\n      }\n    }\n  </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n","path":"/home/robot/.openclaw/workspace-family_consumption_intent/test.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":6939,"output":3197,"cacheRead":9179,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19315,"cost":{"input":0.0020816999999999997,"output":0.0038364,"cacheRead":0.00027537,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.006193469999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773377960143}}
