{"type":"message","id":"c46f1785","parentId":"50de2ad3","timestamp":"2026-03-13T05:15:22.846Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Done. Let me also update the test response to reflect this change.","thinkingSignature":"e9b2e578191088cb7b5ca920998209a50a61f5a651e434232549e503d167c567"},{"type":"text","text":"已更新 AGENTS.md，主要修改：\n\n**1. 第7节 - 个性化推荐**\n- ⚠️ 强调必须结合家庭画像\n- ❌ 禁止推荐具体产品\n- ✅ 只提供选购建议和注意事项\n\n**2. 第10节 - 行为原则**\n- ⚠️ 补充：禁止推荐具体产品型号，只提供选购方向\n\n现在我来用新方式回复你的问题：\n\n---\n\n根据你提供的信息：\n- 场景：节日送礼\n- 对象：孩子\n- 预算：500左右\n- 商品：手表\n\n**选购建议：**\n\n1. **安全第一** - 建议选择有GPS定位功能的手表，保障孩子安全\n\n2. **耐用性** - 孩子使用的东西容易磕碰，选择防水防摔的款式\n\n3. **续航重要** - 续航时间长的手表更实用，减少充电烦恼\n\n4. **根据家庭消费风格** - 如果偏节俭，可以选择性价比高的米兔；如果偏理性，可以选择华为等品牌\n\n你需要告诉我你的**家庭消费风格**（节俭/理性/适度/大方），我可以给出更精准的建议～"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":30774,"output":250,"cacheRead":9179,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40203,"cost":{"input":0.0092322,"output":0.0003,"cacheRead":0.00027537,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00980757}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773378915376}}
{"type":"message","id":"8cc0cccc","parentId":"c46f1785","timestamp":"2026-03-13T05:16:46.347Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b540d951d44a4c32427ce88cf391\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_d0f1627a7a508d84d750914fbb6a2fc2\",\n  \"sender\": \"吴海超\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-03-13 13:16 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"吴海超 (ou_d0f1627a7a508d84d750914fbb6a2fc2)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_d0f1627a7a508d84d750914fbb6a2fc2\",\n  \"name\": \"吴海超\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b540d951d44a4c32427ce88cf391]\n吴海超: 必须项是消费对象，商品，有这两个就可以给出意图识别的结果，把要求写道AGENGT.md"}],"timestamp":1773379006346}}
{"type":"message","id":"9230e5c2","parentId":"8cc0cccc","timestamp":"2026-03-13T05:16:57.354Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求：必须项是消费对象和商品，只要有这两个字段就可以给出意图识别结果。我需要把这个要求写到 AGENTS.md 中。\n\n需要修改槽位检查的逻辑，说明 target（消费对象）和 object（商品）是必填的，其他是可选的。","thinkingSignature":"fc66148142e1cc2d24bcefa6d9cb5470c7c2dc7fe93e3bde0686515b67418b8b"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_3w7ct9pmig50_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"newText":"------------------------------------------------------------\n4. Slot 结构\n------------------------------------------------------------\n\n消费意图需要解析为 Slot 结构：\n\nintent_type\ntarget\nobject\nscene\nbudget\ntime\n\n\n示例：\n\n{\n  \"intent_type\": \"education\",\n  \"target\": \"child\",\n  \"object\": \"schoolbag\",\n  \"scene\": \"school\",\n  \"budget\": null,\n  \"time\": \"soon\"\n}\n\n\n字段说明：\n\nintent_type   必填  消费类型\ntarget        必填  购买对象（谁使用）\nobject        必填  商品（买什么）\nscene         可选  使用场景\nbudget        可选  预算\ntime          可选  时间\n\n\n⚠️ 重要：target（消费对象）和 object（商品）是必填字段！\n\n只要同时具备 target 和 object两个字段，就可以给出意图识别结果，无需等待其他字段完善。","old_string":"------------------------------------------------------------\n4. Slot 结构\n------------------------------------------------------------\n\n消费意图需要解析为 Slot 结构：\n\nintent_type\ntarget\nobject\nscene\nbudget\ntime\n\n\n示例：\n\n{\n  \"intent_type\": \"education\",\n  \"target\": \"child\",\n  \"object\": \"schoolbag\",\n  \"scene\": \"school\",\n  \"budget\": null,\n  \"time\": \"soon\"\n}\n\n\n字段说明：\n\nintent_type   必填  消费类型\ntarget        必填  购买对象\nobject        可选  商品\nscene         可选  使用场景\nbudget        可选  预算\ntime          可选  时间","path":"/home/robot/.openclaw/workspace-family_consumption_intent/AGENTS.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":20,"output":421,"cacheRead":37921,"cacheWrite":2356,"totalTokens":40718,"cost":{"input":0.000006,"output":0.0005052,"cacheRead":0.00113763,"cacheWrite":0.00028272,"total":0.00193155}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773379006346}}
