{"type":"message","id":"a007f27e","parentId":"9859a525","timestamp":"2026-03-13T05:17:06.069Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Done. Now I should also update section 5 (槽位检查) to reflect this change - when target and object are present, no need to ask more questions.","thinkingSignature":"de9fe99357819d7356cf20b252f00950fbc3b6e3b02d579459d3519370307c82"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_s10hbctg4evi_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"newText":"------------------------------------------------------------\n5. 槽位检查\n------------------------------------------------------------\n\n如果关键字段缺失，需要自动追问。\n\n⚠️ 重点：只有当缺少 target（消费对象）或 object（商品）时才追问！\n\n当同时具备 target 和 object 时，视为信息完整，可以直接给出建议。\n\n\n追问规则：\n\n- 优先确认消费对象（target）\n- 其次确认商品（object）\n- 预算、场景、时间可后续补充\n- 一次只问 1-2 个问题\n\n\n示例：\n\n用户：\n想买手机\n\nAgent：\n给谁买手机？\n\n1️⃣ 自己  \n2️⃣ 孩子  \n3️⃣ 家里人  \n\n\n用户：\n给孩子\n\nAgent：（无需再问，可以直接识别为孩子使用手机的意图）\n\n消费对象：孩子\n商品：手机\n意图类型：digital（数码产品）\n\n\n用户：\n给孩子买手机\n\nAgent：（直接识别）\n\n消费对象：孩子\n商品：手机\n意图类型：digital","old_string":"------------------------------------------------------------\n5. 槽位检查\n------------------------------------------------------------\n\n如果关键字段缺失，需要自动追问。\n\n缺失字段示例：\n\ntarget\nbudget\nobject\ntime\n\n\n追问规则：\n\n一次只问 1-2 个问题。\n\n\n示例：\n\n用户：\n想买手机\n\nAgent：\n\n给谁买手机？\n\n1️⃣ 自己  \n2️⃣ 孩子  \n3️⃣ 家里人  \n\n\n用户：\n给孩子\n\nAgent：\n\n预算大概多少？\n\n1️⃣ 1000 以下  \n2️⃣ 1000-3000  \n3️⃣ 3000 以上","path":"/home/robot/.openclaw/workspace-family_consumption_intent/AGENTS.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":31577,"output":396,"cacheRead":9179,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":41152,"cost":{"input":0.0094731,"output":0.0004752,"cacheRead":0.00027537,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01022367}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773379017358}}
