{"type":"message","id":"287aba2e","parentId":"319121e4","timestamp":"2026-03-13T05:19:44.004Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b540da83810a4c12a09fdbb0f3da\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_d0f1627a7a508d84d750914fbb6a2fc2\",\n  \"sender\": \"吴海超\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-03-13 13:19 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"吴海超 (ou_d0f1627a7a508d84d750914fbb6a2fc2)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_d0f1627a7a508d84d750914fbb6a2fc2\",\n  \"name\": \"吴海超\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b540da83810a4c12a09fdbb0f3da]\n吴海超: 开发一个html做测试，上面是和飞书一样的界面 具有对话框 可以输入图片，下面实时的显示意图识别的结果"}],"timestamp":1773379184003}}
{"type":"message","id":"b6ea5520","parentId":"287aba2e","timestamp":"2026-03-13T05:21:32.589Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to develop an HTML page for testing, with a Feishu-like interface (which has a chat interface with an input box that can input text and images), and display the real-time intent recognition results below.\n\nLet me create this HTML page.","thinkingSignature":"6b5c58ebce025af3cd742252822cbeaa22b2b4834c90a46e302e3e173f95df78"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_64p60udjz0us_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n  <title>家庭消费意图识别助手 - 测试</title>\n  <style>\n    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }\n    \n    :root {\n      --primary-color: #1E88E5;\n      --bg-color: #F7F9FB;\n      --border-color: #E8EAED;\n      --text-primary: #333333;\n      --text-secondary: #666666;\n    }\n    \n    body {\n      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'PingFang SC', sans-serif;\n      background: var(--bg-color);\n      height: 100vh;\n      display: flex;\n      flex-direction: column;\n    }\n    \n    /* 顶部导航 - 飞书风格 */\n    .header {\n      background: #fff;\n      padding: 12px 20px;\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);\n      box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\n    }\n    .header-avatar {\n      width: 32px;\n      height: 32px;\n      border-radius: 8px;\n      background: var(--primary-color);\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      justify-content: center;\n      color: white;\n      font-weight: 500;\n      margin-right: 12px;\n    }\n    .header-info h1 {\n      font-size: 14px;\n      color: var(--text-primary);\n      font-weight: 500;\n    }\n    .header-info span {\n      font-size: 12px;\n      color: var(--text-secondary);\n    }\n    .header-status {\n      margin-left: auto;\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      gap: 6px;\n      font-size: 12px;\n      color: #52C41A;\n    }\n    .status-dot {\n      width: 8px;\n      height: 8px;\n      border-radius: 50%;\n      background: #52C41A;\n    }\n    \n    /* 主内容区 */\n    .main-container {\n      flex: 1;\n      display: flex;\n      overflow: hidden;\n    }\n    \n    /* 左侧聊天区 */\n    .chat-section {\n      flex: 1;\n      display: flex;\n      flex-direction: column;\n      background: #fff;\n      border-right: 1px solid var(--border-color);\n    }\n    \n    .chat-messages {\n      flex: 1;\n      overflow-y: auto;\n      padding: 20px;\n    }\n    \n    .message {\n      display: flex;\n      margin-bottom: 20px;\n      align-items: flex-start;\n    }\n    .message.user {\n      flex-direction: row-reverse;\n    }\n    \n    .message-avatar {\n      width: 36px;\n      height: 36px;\n      border-radius: 8px;\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      justify-content: center;\n      font-size: 16px;\n      flex-shrink: 0;\n    }\n    .user .message-avatar {\n      background: var(--primary-color);\n      color: white;\n      margin-left: 12px;\n    }\n    .bot .message-avatar {\n      background: #E8EAED;\n      color: var(--text-secondary);\n      margin-right: 12px;\n    }\n    \n    .message-content {\n      max-width: 70%;\n    }\n    \n    .message-bubble {\n      padding: 12px 16px;\n      border-radius: 8px;\n      font-size: 14px;\n      line-height: 1.5;\n      word-wrap: break-word;\n    }\n    .user .message-bubble {\n      background: var(--primary-color);\n      color: white;\n      border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\n    }\n    .bot .message-bubble {\n      background: #F7F9FB;\n      color: var(--text-primary);\n      border: 1px solid var(--border-color);\n      border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\n    }\n    \n    .message-image {\n      max-width: 200px;\n      border-radius: 8px;\n      margin-top: 8px;\n    }\n    \n    .message-time {\n      font-size: 11px;\n      color: var(--text-secondary);\n      margin-top: 4px;\n    }\n    .user .message-time {\n      text-align: right;\n    }\n    \n    /* 输入区 - 飞书风格 */\n    .input-area {\n      padding: 16px 20px;\n      border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);\n      background: #fff;\n    }\n    \n    .input-wrapper {\n      border: 1px solid var(--border-color);\n      border-radius: 8px;\n      overflow: hidden;\n      transition: border-color 0.2s;\n    }\n    .input-wrapper:focus-within {\n      border-color: var(--primary-color);\n    }\n    \n    .input-textarea {\n      width: 100%;\n      min-height: 80px;\n      padding: 12px;\n      border: none;\n      resize: none;\n      font-size: 14px;\n      font-family: inherit;\n      outline: none;\n    }\n    \n    .input-toolbar {\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      justify-content: space-between;\n      padding: 8px 12px;\n      background: #F7F9FB;\n      border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);\n    }\n    \n    .toolbar-left {\n      display: flex;\n      gap: 12px;\n    }\n    \n    .toolbar-btn {\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      gap: 4px;\n      padding: 4px 8px;\n      border: none;\n      background: none;\n      cursor: pointer;\n      color: var(--text-secondary);\n      font-size: 13px;\n      border-radius: 4px;\n      transition: all 0.2s;\n    }\n    .toolbar-btn:hover {\n      background: #E8EAED;\n      color: var(--text-primary);\n    }\n    \n    .send-btn {\n      padding: 6px 16px;\n      background: var(--primary-color);\n      color: white;\n      border: none;\n      border-radius: 4px;\n      cursor: pointer;\n      font-size: 13px;\n      font-weight: 500;\n      transition: background 0.2s;\n    }\n    .send-btn:hover {\n      background: #1976D2;\n    }\n    .send-btn:disabled {\n      background: #BDBDBD;\n      cursor: not-allowed;\n    }\n    \n    /* 右侧结果区 */\n    .result-section {\n      width: 380px;\n      background: #fff;\n      display: flex;\n      flex-direction: column;\n    }\n    \n    .result-header {\n      padding: 16px 20px;\n      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);\n      font-size: 14px;\n      font-weight: 500;\n      color: var(--text-primary);\n    }\n    \n    .result-content {\n      flex: 1;\n      overflow-y: auto;\n      padding: 16px;\n    }\n    \n    .result-card {\n      background: #F7F9FB;\n      border-radius: 8px;\n      padding: 16px;\n      margin-bottom: 12px;\n    }\n    \n    .result-card-title {\n      font-size: 13px;\n      font-weight: 500;\n      color: var(--text-secondary);\n      margin-bottom: 10px;\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      gap: 6px;\n    }\n    \n    .result-tag {\n      display: inline-flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      padding: 4px 10px;\n      background: #E3F2FD;\n      color: var(--primary-color);\n      border-radius: 4px;\n      font-size: 12px;\n      margin: 2px;\n    }\n    .result-tag strong {\n      font-weight: 500;\n    }\n    \n    .result-detail {\n      margin-top: 8px;\n      font-size: 13px;\n      color: var(--text-primary);\n    }\n    .result-detail-item {\n      display: flex;\n      padding: 6px 0;\n      border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;\n    }\n    .result-detail-item:last-child {\n      border-bottom: none;\n    }\n    .result-label {\n      width: 70px;\n      color: var(--text-secondary);\n      flex-shrink: 0;\n    }\n    .result-value {\n      flex: 1;\n      color: var(--text-primary);\n    }\n    \n    .result-empty {\n      text-align: center;\n      padding: 40px 20px;\n      color: var(--text-secondary);\n    }\n    .result-empty-icon {\n      font-size: 32px;\n      margin-bottom: 12px;\n    }\n    \n    /* 思考中动画 */\n    .thinking {\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      gap: 8px;\n      color: var(--text-secondary);\n      font-size: 13px;\n      padding: 8px 0;\n    }\n    .thinking-dots {\n      display: flex;\n      gap: 4px;\n    }\n    .thinking-dots span {\n      width: 6px;\n      height: 6px;\n      background: var(--text-secondary);\n      border-radius: 50%;\n      animation: bounce 1.4s infinite ease-in-out;\n    }\n    .thinking-dots span:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: -0.32s; }\n    .thinking-dots span:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: -0.16s; }\n    @keyframes bounce {\n      0%, 80%, 100% { transform: scale(0); }\n      40% { transform: scale(1); }\n    }\n    \n    /* 图片预览 */\n    .image-preview {\n      position: fixed;\n      top: 0;\n      left: 0;\n      right: 0;\n      bottom: 0;\n      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.8);\n      display: none;\n      align-items: center;\n      justify-content: center;\n      z-index: 1000;\n    }\n    .image-preview.show {\n      display: flex;\n    }\n    .image-preview img {\n      max-width: 90%;\n      max-height: 90%;\n      border-radius: 8px;\n    }\n    .image-preview-close {\n      position: absolute;\n      top: 20px;\n      right: 20px;\n      color: white;\n      font-size: 24px;\n      cursor: pointer;\n    }\n    \n    /* 隐藏文件输入 */\n    #imageInput {\n      display: none;\n    }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <!-- 顶部导航 -->\n  <div class=\"header\">\n    <div class=\"header-avatar\">🤖</div>\n    <div class=\"header-info\">\n      <h1>家庭消费意图识别助手</h1>\n      <span>AI Assistant</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"header-status\">\n      <span class=\"status-dot\"></span>\n      在线\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  \n  <!-- 主内容区 -->\n  <div class=\"main-container\">\n    <!-- 左侧聊天区 -->\n    <div class=\"chat-section\">\n      <div class=\"chat-messages\" id=\"chatMessages\">\n        <!-- 欢迎消息 -->\n        <div class=\"message bot\">\n          <div class=\"message-avatar\">🤖</div>\n          <div class=\"message-content\">\n            <div class=\"message-bubble\">\n              你好！我是家庭消费意图识别助手 🎯\n              <br><br>\n              告诉我你想买什么，我可以帮你：\n              <br>• 识别消费意图\n              <br>• 分析需求\n              <br>• 给出选购建议\n              <br><br>\n              可以发文字或图片试试~\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"message-time\">今天 13:19</div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <!-- 输入区 -->\n      <div class=\"input-area\">\n        <div class=\"input-wrapper\">\n          <textarea class=\"input-textarea\" id=\"messageInput\" placeholder=\"输入消息...\"></textarea>\n          <div class=\"input-toolbar\">\n            <div class=\"toolbar-left\">\n              <button class=\"toolbar-btn\" onclick=\"document.getElementById('imageInput').click()\">\n                🖼️ 图片\n              </button>\n              <button class=\"toolbar-btn\" onclick=\"clearChat()\">\n                🗑️ 清空\n              </button>\n            </div>\n            <button class=\"send-btn\" id=\"sendBtn\" onclick=\"sendMessage()\">发送</button>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <input type=\"file\" id=\"imageInput\" accept=\"image/*\" onchange=\"handleImageSelect(event)\">\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    \n    <!-- 右侧结果区 -->\n    <div class=\"result-section\">\n      <div class=\"result-header\">🎯 实时意图识别结果</div>\n      <div class=\"result-content\" id=\"resultContent\">\n        <div class=\"result-empty\">\n          <div class=\"result-empty-icon\">📋</div>\n          <div>发送消息后显示识别结果</div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  \n  <!-- 图片预览 -->\n  <div class=\"image-preview\" id=\"imagePreview\" onclick=\"closeImagePreview()\">\n    <span class=\"image-preview-close\">✕</span>\n    <img id=\"previewImg\" src=\"\" alt=\"预览\">\n  </div>\n\n  <script>\n    const API_URL = 'http://127.0.0.1:3847/api/chat';\n    let currentImage = null;\n    \n    // 发送消息\n    async function sendMessage() {\n      const input = document.getElementById('messageInput');\n      const message = input.value.trim();\n      \n      if (!message && !currentImage) return;\n      \n      const sendBtn = document.getElementById('sendBtn');\n      sendBtn.disabled = true;\n      \n      // 添加用户消息\n      addUserMessage(message, currentImage);\n      \n      // 显示思考中\n      showThinking();\n      \n      input.value = '';\n      currentImage = null;\n      \n      try {\n        const response = await fetch(API_URL, {\n          method: 'POST',\n          headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },\n          body: JSON.stringify({\n            message: message || '（图片消息）',\n            userId: 'wuhaichao',\n            familyId: 'default',\n            image: currentImage\n          })\n        });\n        \n        const data = await response.json();\n        \n        // 移除思考中\n        removeThinking();\n        \n        // 添加机器人回复\n        addBotMessage(data);\n        \n        // 更新识别结果\n        updateResult(data);\n        \n      } catch (error) {\n        removeThinking();\n        addBotMessage({ error: error.message });\n      } finally {\n        sendBtn.disabled = false;\n        document.getElementById('messageInput').focus();\n      }\n    }\n    \n    // 添加用户消息\n    function addUserMessage(text, image) {\n      const container = document.getElementById('chatMessages');\n      const time = new Date().toLocaleTimeString('zh-CN', { hour: '2-digit', minute: '2-digit' });\n      \n      let html = `<div class=\"message user\">\n        <div class=\"message-avatar\">😊</div>\n        <div class=\"message-content\">\n          <div class=\"message-bubble\">${text || ''}</div>\n          ${image ? `<img src=\"${image}\" class=\"message-image\" onclick=\"showImagePreview('${image}')\">` : ''}\n          <div class=\"message-time\">今天 ${time}</div>\n        </div>\n      </div>`;\n      \n      container.insertAdjacentHTML('beforeend', html);\n      container.scrollTop = container.scrollHeight;\n    }\n    \n    // 添加机器人消息\n    function addBotMessage(data) {\n      const container = document.getElementById('chatMessages');\n      const time = new Date().toLocaleTimeString('zh-CN', { hour: '2-digit', minute: '2-digit' });\n      \n      let reply = data.reply || '';\n      \n      if (data.error) {\n        reply = `❌ 错误: ${data.error}`;\n      }\n      \n      let html = `<div class=\"message bot\">\n        <div class=\"message-avatar\">🤖</div>\n        <div class=\"message-content\">\n          <div class=\"message-bubble\">${reply}</div>\n          <div class=\"message-time\">今天 ${time}</div>\n        </div>\n      </div>`;\n      \n      container.insertAdjacentHTML('beforeend', html);\n      container.scrollTop = container.scrollHeight;\n    }\n    \n    // 显示思考中\n    function showThinking() {\n      const container = document.getElementById('chatMessages');\n      container.insertAdjacentHTML('beforeend', `\n        <div class=\"message bot\" id=\"thinkingMsg\">\n          <div class=\"message-avatar\">🤖</div>\n          <div class=\"message-content\">\n            <div class=\"thinking\">\n              <div class=\"thinking-dots\">\n                <span></span><span></span><span></span>\n              </div>\n              识别中...\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      `);\n      container.scrollTop = container.scrollHeight;\n    }\n    \n    // 移除思考中\n    function removeThinking() {\n      const el = document.getElementById('thinkingMsg');\n      if (el) el.remove();\n    }\n    \n    // 更新识别结果\n    function updateResult(data) {\n      const container = document.getElementById('resultContent');\n      \n      if (data.error) {\n        container.innerHTML = `<div class=\"result-card\" style=\"border:1px solid #ff4d4f;\">\n          <div class=\"result-card-title\" style=\"color:#ff4d4f;\">❌ 错误</div>\n          <div class=\"result-detail\">${data.error}</div>\n        </div>`;\n        return;\n      }\n      \n      const intent = data.intent || {};\n      const currentIntent = data.current_intent || {};\n      const nextQuestion = data.next_question;\n      \n      let html = '';\n      \n      // 意图识别\n      html += `<div class=\"result-card\">\n        <div class=\"result-card-title\">🎯 意图识别</div>\n        <div>\n          <span class=\"result-tag\"><strong>类型:</strong> ${intent.intent_type || '-'}</span>\n          <span class=\"result-tag\"><strong>目标:</strong> ${currentIntent.target || '-'}</span>\n          <span class=\"result-tag\"><strong>商品:</strong> ${currentIntent.object || '-'}</span>\n          <span class=\"result-tag\"><strong>时间:</strong> ${currentIntent.time || '-'}</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>`;\n      \n      // 详细信息\n      if (Object.keys(currentIntent).length > 0) {\n        html += `<div class=\"result-card\">\n          <div class=\"result-card-title\">📋 槽位信息</div>\n          <div class=\"result-detail\">\n            ${currentIntent.target ? `<div class=\"result-detail-item\"><span class=\"result-label\">消费对象</span><span class=\"result-value\">${currentIntent.target}</span></div>` : ''}\n            ${currentIntent.object ? `<div class=\"result-detail-item\"><span class=\"result-label\">商品</span><span class=\"result-value\">${currentIntent.object}</span></div>` : ''}\n            ${currentIntent.scene ? `<div class=\"result-detail-item\"><span class=\"result-label\">场景</span><span class=\"result-value\">${currentIntent.scene}</span></div>` : ''}\n            ${currentIntent.budget ? `<div class=\"result-detail-item\"><span class=\"result-label\">预算</span><span class=\"result-value\">${currentIntent.budget}</span></div>` : ''}\n            ${currentIntent.time ? `<div class=\"result-detail-item\"><span class=\"result-label\">时间</span><span class=\"result-value\">${currentIntent.time}</span></div>` : ''}\n            ${currentIntent.is_complete !== undefined ? `<div class=\"result-detail-item\"><span class=\"result-label\">信息完整</span><span class=\"result-value\">${currentIntent.is_complete ? '是' : '否'}</span></div>` : ''}\n          </div>\n        </div>`;\n      }\n      \n      // 追问\n      if (nextQuestion) {\n        html += `<div class=\"result-card\">\n          <div class=\"result-card-title\">💬 追问</div>\n          <div class=\"result-detail\">\n            <div class=\"result-detail-item\">\n              <span class=\"result-label\">问题</span>\n              <span class=\"result-value\">${nextQuestion.question || '-'}</span>\n            </div>\n            ${nextQuestion.options ? `<div class=\"result-detail-item\"><span class=\"result-label\">选项</span><span class=\"result-value\">${nextQuestion.options.map(o => o.value).join(', ')}</span></div>` : ''}\n          </div>\n        </div>`;\n      }\n      \n      // 推荐\n      if (data.recommendations && data.recommendations.length > 0) {\n        html += `<div class=\"result-card\">\n          <div class=\"result-card-title\">💡 推荐</div>\n          <div class=\"result-detail\">\n            ${data.recommendations.map(r => `<div>• <strong>${r.name}</strong>: ${r.reason || ''}</div>`).join('')}\n          </div>\n        </div>`;\n      }\n      \n      // 原始数据\n      html += `<div class=\"result-card\">\n        <div class=\"result-card-title\">📦 原始数据</div>\n        <pre style=\"font-size:11px;overflow-x:auto;background:#fff;padding:8px;border-radius:4px;\">${JSON.stringify(data, null, 2)}</pre>\n      </div>`;\n      \n      container.innerHTML = html;\n    }\n    \n    // 处理图片选择\n    function handleImageSelect(event) {\n      const file = event.target.files[0];\n      if (!file) return;\n      \n      const reader = new FileReader();\n      reader.onload = function(e) {\n        currentImage = e.target.result;\n        // 显示图片预览在输入框\n        const input = document.getElementById('messageInput');\n        input.value += '[图片] ';\n      };\n      reader.readAsDataURL(file);\n      \n      event.target.value = '';\n    }\n    \n    // 清空聊天\n    function clearChat() {\n      document.getElementById('chatMessages').innerHTML = `\n        <div class=\"message bot\">\n          <div class=\"message-avatar\">🤖</div>\n          <div class=\"message-content\">\n            <div class=\"message-bubble\">\n              对话已清空，请继续发送消息~\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"message-time\">今天 ${new Date().toLocaleTimeString('zh-CN', { hour: '2-digit', minute: '2-digit' })}</div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      `;\n      document.getElementById('resultContent').innerHTML = `\n        <div class=\"result-empty\">\n          <div class=\"result-empty-icon\">📋</div>\n          <div>发送消息后显示识别结果</div>\n        </div>\n      `;\n    }\n    \n    // 图片预览\n    function showImagePreview(src) {\n      document.getElementById('previewImg').src = src;\n      document.getElementById('imagePreview').classList.add('show');\n    }\n    \n    function closeImagePreview() {\n      document.getElementById('imagePreview').classList.remove('show');\n    }\n    \n    // 回车发送\n    document.getElementById('messageInput').addEventListener('keydown', function(e) {\n      if (e.key === 'Enter' && !e.shiftKey) {\n        e.preventDefault();\n        sendMessage();\n      }\n    });\n  </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n","path":"/home/robot/.openclaw/workspace-family_consumption_intent/test_v2.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":20,"output":5381,"cacheRead":41309,"cacheWrite":1411,"totalTokens":48121,"cost":{"input":0.000006,"output":0.0064572,"cacheRead":0.0012392699999999998,"cacheWrite":0.00016931999999999998,"total":0.00787179}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773379184004}}
