{"type":"message","id":"82a87472","parentId":"fb75f325","timestamp":"2026-03-13T05:21:49.385Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The API is working. Let me provide the user with the URL and a description.","thinkingSignature":"99b51a2373e2518f90d94588cd17bec9b2d8eab41a7f5fcab12661be20f41c7b"},{"type":"text","text":"已创建新测试页面 `test_v2.html`！\n\n**访问地址：** `http://192.168.3.33:8889/test_v2.html`\n\n---\n\n**界面特点：**\n\n1. **飞书风格界面**\n   - 顶部：头像 + 助手名称 + 在线状态\n   - 左侧：聊天对话框（支持文字 + 图片）\n   - 右侧：实时意图识别结果\n\n2. **功能**\n   - 输入文字发送消息\n   - 点击🖼️图片按钮选择图片\n   - 发送后右侧实时显示识别结果\n   - 支持清空对话\n\n3. **右侧结果显示**\n   - 🎯 意图识别（类型、目标、商品、时间）\n   - 📋 槽位信息（消费对象、商品、场景、预算等）\n   - 💬 追问（当前问题+选项）\n   - 💡 推荐\n   - 📦 原始JSON数据\n\n---\n\n测试一下：发送\"给孩子买手表\"看看效果 😊"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":39650,"output":226,"cacheRead":9179,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49055,"cost":{"input":0.011895,"output":0.0002712,"cacheRead":0.00027537,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.012441569999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773379303570}}
