{"type":"message","id":"7d4650e7","parentId":"bf11a319","timestamp":"2026-03-13T05:28:45.017Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying \"我想买个礼物\" (I want to buy a gift). According to the updated AGENTS.md rules:\n\n- Required fields: target (consumer) + object (product)\n- If both are present → direct recognition, no follow-up questions\n- Scene/budget → auto-predict based on family profile\n\nCurrently:\n- target: self (自动识别为\"自己\")\n- object: gift (礼物) - wait, the user said \"礼物\" which means gift, but is that the object?\n\nActually, \"礼物\" (gift) is more of a scene/purpose rather than a specific product. The system should ask what kind of gift.\n\nBut wait - the user is just saying the same thing again \"我想买礼物\". Let me test this with the API to see what happens.","thinkingSignature":"02a0255ad58ccc26caad6afd46cdba5dadae303b6af8ab0f9f9c4a7b01ff7f65"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_kmze7rvh0ryx_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -X POST http://127.0.0.1:3847/api/chat -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"message\":\"我想买个礼物\",\"userId\":\"wuhaichao\",\"familyId\":\"default\"}' --noproxy \"*\" | python3 -m json.tool","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":20,"output":265,"cacheRead":52749,"cacheWrite":2169,"totalTokens":55203,"cost":{"input":0.000006,"output":0.000318,"cacheRead":0.0015824699999999999,"cacheWrite":0.00026028,"total":0.00216675}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773379703762}}
{"type":"message","id":"18880893","parentId":"7d4650e7","timestamp":"2026-03-13T05:28:45.039Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_kmze7rvh0ryx_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n    \"intent\": {\n        \"intent_type\": null,\n        \"object\": null,\n        \"target\": \"\\u81ea\\u5df1\",\n        \"scene\": null,\n        \"budget\": null,\n        \"time\": \"future\",\n        \"is_complete\": false\n    },\n    \"current_intent\": {\n        \"intent_type\": null,\n        \"object\": null,\n        \"target\": \"\\u81ea\\u5df1\",\n        \"scene\": null,\n        \"budget\": null,\n        \"time\": \"future\",\n        \"is_complete\": false\n    },\n    \"is_complete\": false,\n    \"missing_fields\": [\n        \"object\",\n        \"scene\"\n    ],\n    \"next_question\": {\n        \"field\": \"scene\",\n        \"question\": \"\\u662f\\u4ec0\\u4e48\\u573a\\u666f\\uff1f\",\n        \"options\": [\n            {\n                \"value\": \"\\u65e5\\u5e38\",\n                \"label\": \"1. \\u65e5\\u5e38\\u4f7f\\u7528\"\n            },\n            {\n                \"value\": \"\\u5f00\\u5b66\",\n                \"label\": \"2. \\u5f00\\u5b66\\u5b63\"\n            },\n            {\n                \"value\": \"\\u8282\\u65e5\",\n                \"label\": \"3. \\u8282\\u65e5\\u9001\\u793c\"\n            },\n            {\n                \"value\": \"\\u574f\\u4e86\",\n                \"label\": \"4. \\u574f\\u4e86\\u8981\\u6362\"\n            },\n            {\n                \"value\": \"\\u4fc3\\u9500\",\n                \"label\": \"5. \\u4fc3\\u9500\\u6d3b\\u52a8\"\n            }\n        ]\n    },\n    \"recommendations\": []\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":20,"aggregated":"{\n    \"intent\": {\n        \"intent_type\": null,\n        \"object\": null,\n        \"target\": \"\\u81ea\\u5df1\",\n        \"scene\": null,\n        \"budget\": null,\n        \"time\": \"future\",\n        \"is_complete\": false\n    },\n    \"current_intent\": {\n        \"intent_type\": null,\n        \"object\": null,\n        \"target\": \"\\u81ea\\u5df1\",\n        \"scene\": null,\n        \"budget\": null,\n        \"time\": \"future\",\n        \"is_complete\": false\n    },\n    \"is_complete\": false,\n    \"missing_fields\": [\n        \"object\",\n        \"scene\"\n    ],\n    \"next_question\": {\n        \"field\": \"scene\",\n        \"question\": \"\\u662f\\u4ec0\\u4e48\\u573a\\u666f\\uff1f\",\n        \"options\": [\n            {\n                \"value\": \"\\u65e5\\u5e38\",\n                \"label\": \"1. \\u65e5\\u5e38\\u4f7f\\u7528\"\n            },\n            {\n                \"value\": \"\\u5f00\\u5b66\",\n                \"label\": \"2. \\u5f00\\u5b66\\u5b63\"\n            },\n            {\n                \"value\": \"\\u8282\\u65e5\",\n                \"label\": \"3. \\u8282\\u65e5\\u9001\\u793c\"\n            },\n            {\n                \"value\": \"\\u574f\\u4e86\",\n                \"label\": \"4. \\u574f\\u4e86\\u8981\\u6362\"\n            },\n            {\n                \"value\": \"\\u4fc3\\u9500\",\n                \"label\": \"5. \\u4fc3\\u9500\\u6d3b\\u52a8\"\n            }\n        ]\n    },\n    \"recommendations\": []\n}","cwd":"/home/robot/.openclaw/workspace-family_consumption_intent"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773379725038}}
{"type":"message","id":"81e8c82b","parentId":"18880893","timestamp":"2026-03-13T05:29:02.219Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The API is treating \"礼物\" (gift) as not a specific object - it's asking about scene (场景) instead. \n\nBut according to the updated AGENTS.md:\n- Only ask when missing target or object\n- Once both target + object exist, give recognition directly\n- Scene/budget should be auto-predicted from family profile\n\nThe issue is:\n1. \"礼物\" is being recognized as target=自己 (self) but object is still null\n2. The API is asking about scene, but it should be asking about object (具体买什么礼物)\n\nWait, actually \"礼物\" could be considered the object. But the system doesn't recognize it as a specific product. Let me check - it says missing_fields includes \"object\".\n\nThe problem is: \"礼物\" is not a specific enough product. The system needs to ask what KIND of gift.\n\nBut according to the rules, we should only ask for target and object. Since target is already \"自己\", we should ask for object - what specific gift.\n\nSo the question should be \"想买什么礼物？\" not \"是什么场景？\"\n\nThis is a backend issue with the intent detection. But let me work with what we have - I should explain to the user that we need to know what specific gift they're looking for.","thinkingSignature":"f48a18168b5d461433a813cd854cb8e06bf1aecf1c32957b30952019ac5453c4"},{"type":"text","text":"根据最新规则，现在应该问\"买什么\"而不是\"什么场景\"。\n\nAPI目前还在问场景，我来按照新规则调整：\n\n---\n\n根据你的情况：\n- ✅ 消费对象：自己\n- ❓ 商品：礼物（太笼统了）\n\n**具体想买什么礼物？**\n1️⃣ 衣服/裤子\n2️⃣ 手机/电子产品\n3️⃣ 首饰/配饰\n4️⃣ 书籍/文具\n5️⃣ 零食/食品\n6️⃣ 化妆品/护肤品\n\n告诉我具体一样，我来帮你分析～"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":46440,"output":378,"cacheRead":9179,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55997,"cost":{"input":0.013932,"output":0.00045359999999999997,"cacheRead":0.00027537,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01466097}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773379725039}}
{"type":"message","id":"931095de","parentId":"81e8c82b","timestamp":"2026-03-13T05:29:26.949Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b540e45a9eca8c3463a5d1515bfc\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_d0f1627a7a508d84d750914fbb6a2fc2\",\n  \"sender\": \"吴海超\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-03-13 13:29 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"吴海超 (ou_d0f1627a7a508d84d750914fbb6a2fc2)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_d0f1627a7a508d84d750914fbb6a2fc2\",\n  \"name\": \"吴海超\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b540e45a9eca8c3463a5d1515bfc]\n吴海超: 按照新的规则调整"}],"timestamp":1773379766948}}
{"type":"message","id":"9848aec5","parentId":"931095de","timestamp":"2026-03-13T05:29:32.630Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to adjust the API/server to follow the new rules. The new rules are:\n\n1. Only ask questions when missing target (消费对象) or object (商品)\n2. When both target and object are present, no need to ask about budget/scene - predict them from family profile\n3. Scene and budget should be predicted from family profile\n\nThe current API is still asking about \"scene\" first, but according to the new rules, \"object\" should be the priority after \"target\".\n\nLet me check if there's a way to update the API or if I need to find where the server code is located.","thinkingSignature":"45d47d2a234e7ac4870c6b19e846374ab5693a4288d0d302b5249a3f50ae1333"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ced2mztchk5d_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find /home/robot/.openclaw/workspace -name \"*.js\" | head -20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":20,"output":173,"cacheRead":54836,"cacheWrite":934,"totalTokens":55963,"cost":{"input":0.000006,"output":0.00020759999999999998,"cacheRead":0.00164508,"cacheWrite":0.00011207999999999998,"total":0.00197076}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773379766949}}
