{"type":"message","id":"8aa5d5b4","parentId":"4dae655b","timestamp":"2026-03-13T05:31:45.834Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The second test shows that when target is present but object is missing, it correctly asks for object. But the intent_type is \"digital\" (from the keyword \"手机\"), which is good.\n\nWait, in test 2, it shows object: None - that's because \"手机\" is recognized as intent_type but not as object. The processIntent function needs to be updated to also extract the object from the message.\n\nLet me check the processIntent function and update it to properly extract the object.","thinkingSignature":"dc499356d6b5b28002069766dfaba58e81620d9cd7e5386dc241c1032020be8d"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rbxvc3j5wci1_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"newText":"// 简化版：直接在 Node.js 中处理意图识别\nfunction processIntent(text) {\n    const intentKeywords = {\n        \"education\": [\"开学\", \"学习\", \"补习\", \"培训\", \"学校\", \"书包\", \"文具\", \"作业\", \"学费\", \"辅导\"],\n        \"appliance\": [\"冰箱\", \"空调\", \"洗衣机\", \"电视\", \"家电\", \"坏了\", \"维修\", \"换一个\", \"买新的\"],\n        \"food\": [\"吃\", \"水果\", \"零食\", \"买菜\", \"做饭\", \"牛奶\", \"饮料\", \"外卖\", \"餐厅\"],\n        \"daily\": [\"日用品\", \"牙膏\", \"洗衣液\", \"纸巾\", \"洗发水\", \"沐浴露\", \"生活用品\"],\n        \"digital\": [\"手机\", \"电脑\", \"平板\", \"笔记本\", \"耳机\", \"数码\", \"电子产品\"],\n        \"clothing\": [\"衣服\", \"鞋子\", \"裤子\", \"裙子\", \"外套\", \"童装\", \"成人装\"],\n        \"entertainment\": [\"玩具\", \"游戏\", \"旅游\", \"电影\", \"娱乐\", \"周末玩\"],\n        \"health\": [\"体检\", \"药\", \"补品\", \"保健品\", \"医院\", \"身体\", \"看病\"],\n        \"service\": [\"维修\", \"搬家\", \"家政\", \"保洁\", \"服务\", \"安装\"],\n        \"sports\": [\"运动\", \"跑步\", \"健身\", \"球类\", \"游泳\"],\n        \"beauty\": [\"化妆品\", \"护肤品\", \"美容\", \"美发\"],\n        \"pet\": [\"宠物\", \"猫\", \"狗\", \"狗粮\", \"猫粮\"],\n        \"car\": [\"汽车\", \"车\", \"二手车\", \"新车\"]\n    };\n    \n    const targetKeywords = {\n        \"自己\": [\"我\", \"自己\", \"给我\"],\n        \"孩子\": [\"孩子\", \"小孩\", \"儿子\", \"女儿\", \"宝宝\", \"小朋友\", \"儿童\"],\n        \"家庭\": [\"家里\", \"家用\", \"家里用\", \"全家\"],\n        \"父母\": [\"父母\", \"爸爸\", \"妈妈\", \"老人家\", \"老人\", \"公婆\", \"岳父母\"]\n    };\n    \n    const sceneKeywords = {\n        \"开学\": [\"开学\", \"上学\", \"新学期\", \"返校\"],\n        \"节日\": [\"节日\", \"春节\", \"中秋\", \"国庆\", \"生日\", \"过年\"],\n        \"坏了\": [\"坏了\", \"不能用了\"],\n        \"换季\": [\"换季\", \"春天\", \"夏天\", \"冬天\", \"秋天\"],\n        \"促销\": [\"促销\", \"打折\", \"优惠\", \"双11\", \"618\"],\n        \"日常\": [\"日常\", \"平时\", \"平常\"]\n    };\n    \n    // 识别商品类别\n    let intent_type = null;\n    let maxScore = 0;\n    let detectedObject = null;\n    \n    for (const [type, keywords] of Object.entries(intentKeywords)) {\n        const score = keywords.filter(kw => text.includes(kw)).length;\n        if (score > maxScore) {\n            maxScore = score;\n            intent_type = type;\n            // 找出匹配的商品关键词\n            for (const kw of keywords) {\n                if (text.includes(kw)) {\n                    detectedObject = kw;\n                    break;\n                }\n            }\n        }\n    }\n    \n    // 识别消费对象\n    let target = null;\n    for (const [t, keywords] of Object.entries(targetKeywords)) {\n        if (keywords.some(kw => text.includes(kw))) {\n            target = t;\n            break;\n        }\n    }\n    \n    // 识别场景\n    let scene = null;\n    for (const [s, keywords] of Object.entries(sceneKeywords)) {\n        if (keywords.some(kw => text.includes(kw))) {\n            scene = s;\n            break;\n        }\n    }\n    \n    return {\n        intent_type: intent_type,\n        object: detectedObject,  // 从消息中提取商品\n        target: target,\n        scene: scene,\n        budget: null,\n        time: \"future\",\n        is_complete: !!(intent_type && target && detectedObject)\n    };\n}","old_string":"// 简化版：直接在 Node.js 中处理意图识别\nfunction processIntent(text) {\n    const intentKeywords = {\n  