 it would be cleaner to update the API response to make this distinction clear. Let me add a flag or simplify the response.Actually, the simplest approach is to update the API to return a cleaner response. Let me modify the handleChat function.","thinkingSignature":"0528ff60a160977d48154728f53dc4c9e0caf61e3d21d19d705aba83c0b5d3d7"},{"type":"text","text":"已更新 AGENTS.md！\n\n**新规则：**\n- ❌ 信息不完整时：不显示识别结果、槽位、推荐\n- ✅ 只显示追问问题\n- ✅ 信息完整时：显示完整分析和建议\n\n现在调整 API 响应：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9hszoj45kphc_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -n \"return {\" /home/robot/.openclaw/workspace/family-sync-server.js | tail -10"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":72745,"output":556,"cacheRead":9179,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":82480,"cost":{"input":0.0218235,"output":0.0006672,"cacheRead":0.00027537,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02276607}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773380463489}}
