{"type":"message","id":"ca0a230b","parentId":"c923e7ba","timestamp":"2026-03-13T05:44:26.071Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我需要修改逻辑：当用户回复选项时，除了记录选项值，还要同时检查消息中是否包含新的关键词（比如\"孩子\"），如果有就更新。\n\n或者更简单的方案：在 handleChat 中，如果用户发了新的消息（不是选项），就先进行意图识别，然后合并之前的上下文。","thinkingSignature":"c0c2d0c9cb7ce171b28920655bf1ccbf74548c217e48cd65a124b09082a3a99d"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_yd1dt8uupccb_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/robot/.openclaw/workspace/family-sync-server.js","limit":40,"offset":255}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":76865,"output":116,"cacheRead":9179,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":86160,"cost":{"input":0.0230595,"output":0.0001392,"cacheRead":0.00027537,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02347407}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773380661733}}
{"type":"message","id":"bf1ce883","parentId":"ca0a230b","timestamp":"2026-03-13T05:44:26.076Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_yd1dt8uupccb_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"let conversationState = {};\nlet consumptionHistory = {};\n\nasync function handleChat(message, familyId, option = null) {\n    let intent = {};\n    \n    if (message && !option) {\n        // 新消息，进行意图识别\n        intent = processIntent(message);\n        conversationState[familyId] = { intent: intent };\n    } else if (option && conversationState[familyId]) {\n        intent = conversationState[familyId].intent;\n        const lastAsked = conversationState[familyId].lastAsked || 'target';\n        const optIdx = parseInt(option) - 1;\n        \n        if (lastAsked === 'object') {\n            intent.object = option;\n        } else if (!isNaN(optIdx) && optIdx >= 0) {\n            const q = QUESTIONS[lastAsked];\n            if (q && q.options && q.options[optIdx]) {\n                intent[lastAsked] = q.options[optIdx].value;\n            }\n        } else {\n            intent[lastAsked] = option;\n        }\n        \n        conversationState[familyId].lastAsked = null;\n        conversationState[familyId].intent = intent;\n    } else {\n        intent = { object: null, target: null, scene: null };\n    }\n    \n    // 检查完整性 - 只检查必填字段：商品、消费对象\n    const missing = [];\n    if (!intent.object) missing.push(\"object\");\n    if (!intent.target) missing.push(\"target\");\n    \n    const isComplete = missing.length === 0;\n    \n    // 获取家庭数据用于预测\n\n[217 more lines in file. Use offset=295 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773380666074}}
{"type":"message","id":"fa023575","parentId":"bf1ce883","timestamp":"2026-03-13T05:44:39.386Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我看到问题了。当用户直接回复\"电脑\"而不是选择选项时，代码走的是第一个分支（message && !option），这时会重新进行意图识别，但不会保留之前的对话上下文。我需要修改逻辑：1. 每次用户发消息时，都进行意图识别2. 然后如果有之前的上下文，合并它们让我修改代码：","thinkingSignature":"9bdb30be91b064b35867a4ea72b5d1edfb6338f9f47dbe8ec521763dd0ab3860"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_g2vtl4ih12v6_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"newText":"async function handleChat(message, familyId, option = null) {\n    let intent = {};\n    \n    // 优先从消息中提取意图（每次都重新识别，保留最新信息）\n    const newIntent = processIntent(message || option);\n    \n    if (conversationState[familyId]) {\n        // 有历史上下文，合并新旧意图（取最新的非空值）\n        const oldIntent = conversationState[familyId].intent || {};\n        intent = {\n            intent_type: newIntent.intent_type || oldIntent.intent_type,\n            object: newIntent.object || oldIntent.object,\n            target: newIntent.target || oldIntent.target,\n            scene: newIntent.scene || oldIntent.scene,\n            budget: newIntent.budget || oldIntent.budget,\n            time: newIntent.time || oldIntent.time\n        };\n    } else {\n        // 首次对话\n        intent = newIntent;\n    }\n    \n    // 保存上下文\n    conversationState[familyId] = { \n        intent: intent,\n        lastAsked: null\n    };\n    \n    // 检查完整性 - 只检查必填字段：商品、消费对象\n    const missing = [];\n    if (!intent.object) missing.push(\"object\");\n    if (!intent.target) missing.push(\"target\");\n    \n    const isComplete = missing.length === 0;","old_string":"async function handleChat(message, familyId, option = null) {\n    let intent = {};\n    \n    if (message && !option) {\n        // 新消息，进行意图识别\n        intent = processIntent(message);\n        conversationState[familyId] = { intent: intent };\n    } else if (option && conversationState[familyId]) {\n        intent = conversationState[familyId].intent;\n        const lastAsked = conversationState[familyId].lastAsked || 'target';\n        const optIdx = parseInt(option) - 1;\n        \n        if (lastAsked === 'object') {\n            intent.object = option;\n        } else if (!isNaN(optIdx) && optIdx >= 0) {\n            const q = QUESTIONS[lastAsked];\n            if (q && q.options && q.options[optIdx]) {\n                intent[lastAsked] = q.options[optIdx].value;\n            }\n        } else {\n            intent[lastAsked] = option;\n        }\n        \n        conversationState[familyId].lastAsked = null;\n        conversationState[familyId].intent = intent;\n    } else {\n        intent = { object: null, target: null, scene: null };\n    }\n    \n    // 检查完整性 - 只检查必填字段：商品、消费对象\n    const missing = [];\n    if (!intent.object) missing.push(\"object\");\n    if (!intent.target) missing.push(\"target\");\n    \n    const isComplete = missing.length === 0;","path":"/home/robot/.openclaw/workspace/family-sync-server.js"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":77335,"output":702,"cacheRead":9179,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":87216,"cost":{"input":0.0232005,"output":0.0008424,"cacheRead":0.00027537,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02431827}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773380666076}}
