{"type":"message","id":"52d0d7fb","parentId":"86167693","timestamp":"2026-03-13T05:46:32.027Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"完成了。现在给用户确认。","thinkingSignature":"dfb4eca17a57557e7ea81dca051a6f87930abe168f1b619df5c3ef509f5f153d"},{"type":"text","text":"已更新 AGENTS.md！\n\n**新增内容：**\n\n1. **上下文记忆规则**\n   - 自动合并历史对话信息\n   - 不重复询问已确认的信息\n\n2. **正确对话流程示例**\n   - 第1轮：追问商品\n   - 第2轮：自动合并\"孩子+电脑\" → 直接识别\n\n3. **不需要追问的情况**\n   - 同时具备 target 和 object 时直接识别\n\n---\n\n现在的对话流程：\n> 你：我想给孩子买个礼物  \n> 我：想买什么？  \n> 你：电脑  \n> 我：✅ 完整！孩子+电脑，直接给建议\n\n不用再重复说\"孩子\"了 👍"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":81780,"output":145,"cacheRead":9179,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":91104,"cost":{"input":0.024534,"output":0.000174,"cacheRead":0.00027537,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02498337}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773380785069}}
