{"type":"message","id":"20095502","parentId":"f6a93726","timestamp":"2026-03-13T06:19:11.906Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"There are some issues:1. Test 2: \"买空调\" should ask for target, but it's showing complete with target:孩子 (this is carrying over from previous test)2. Test 3: \"给我爸买东西\" should recognize target:父母, but it's showing target:自己3. Test 4: \"想买点什么\" is showing target:自己 and object:空调 (wrong)4. Test 6: \"我想给孩子买个礼物\" is showing complete with object:衣服 (wrong, should be incomplete)5. Test 8: \"开学了给孩子买书包\" - object should be \"书包\" not \"开学\"Let me analyze the issues and provide a summary of results to the user.","thinkingSignature":"50ad55c424b54f9ff6146b9a95cb96f17e3d2c7fa3a2bf069c80efe5f5ca2827"},{"type":"text","text":"测试结果汇总：\n\n| # | 测试用例 | 预期结果 | 实际结果 | 状态 |\n|---|---------|---------|---------|------|\n| 1 | 给孩子买手机 | ✅完整 | ✅ target:孩子, object:手机 | ✅ |\n| 2 | 买空调 | 应追问target | ❌ 错误（上下文残留） | ⚠️ |\n| 3 | 给我爸买东西 | target:父母 | ❌ target:自己 | ❌ |\n| 4 | 想买点什么 | 应追问 | ❌ 错误识别 | ❌ |\n| 5 | 过年给妈妈买件衣服 | ✅完整 | ✅ target:父母, object:衣服, scene:节日 | ✅ |\n| 6 | 我想给孩子买个礼物 | 追问商品 | ❌ 错误识别 | ❌ |\n| 7 | 玩具（连续） | ✅完整 | ✅ target:孩子, object:玩具 | ✅ |\n| 8 | 开学了给孩子买书包 | ✅完整 | ❌ object识别错误 | ❌ |\n| 9 | 坏了想换个冰箱 | ✅完整 | ✅ scene:坏了 | ✅ |\n| 10 | 推荐个电视 | 应追问target | ❌ 错误（上下文残留） | ⚠️ |\n\n---\n\n**问题总结：**\n1. ❌ \"礼物\"、\"买点东西\"等模糊词未识别\n2. ❌ \"开学了\"被错误识别为商品\n3. ❌ 某些测试受上下文影响\n4. ✅ 连续对话功能正常\n\n需要我优化这些识别问题吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":106734,"output":480,"cacheRead":9179,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":116393,"cost":{"input":0.0320202,"output":0.000576,"cacheRead":0.00027537,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.032871569999999996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773382740648}}
