{"type":"message","id":"31271d5a","parentId":"82320a07","timestamp":"2026-03-13T06:22:39.266Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"There's still an issue with test 10 - \"我想买礼物\" is incorrectly identifying \"电视\" as the object. This is because \"电视\" was the last object used in the conversation context, and it's being merged incorrectly.\n\nThe issue is in the handleChat function - when there's previous context, it's merging the old object even when the new message has a vague keyword. Let me check and fix this.\n\nActually, looking at the logic more closely:\n- \"我想买礼物\" should NOT set object to anything (because \"礼物\" is in vagueKeywords)\n- But it's still showing \"电视\" as object - this must be from the previous context\n\nThe problem is in the conversationState merging logic. When the new message has vague keywords and doesn't identify an object, we should NOT use the old object. Let me fix this:","thinkingSignature":"246e38513321c7e914bc9e9f61826aab393f2f38ad0e348f31d6b44f78863f81"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_909ufulv0s83_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/robot/.openclaw/workspace/family-sync-server.js","limit":30,"offset":255}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":113593,"output":227,"cacheRead":9179,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":122999,"cost":{"input":0.0340779,"output":0.0002724,"cacheRead":0.00027537,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.03462567}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773382943132}}
{"type":"message","id":"8ddac4e5","parentId":"31271d5a","timestamp":"2026-03-13T06:22:39.271Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_909ufulv0s83_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        product: b.products[0],\n        price_range: b.price,\n        reason: consumeStyle === \"大方\" ? \"品质优良，值得信赖\" : \"性价比高\"\n    }));\n}\n\n// 内存存储（简化版）\nlet conversationState = {};\nlet consumptionHistory = {};\n\nasync function handleChat(message, familyId, option = null) {\n    let intent = {};\n    \n    // 优先从消息中提取意图（每次都重新识别，保留最新信息）\n    const newIntent = processIntent(message || option);\n    \n    if (conversationState[familyId]) {\n        // 有历史上下文，合并新旧意图（取最新的非空值）\n        const oldIntent = conversationState[familyId].intent || {};\n        intent = {\n            intent_type: newIntent.intent_type || oldIntent.intent_type,\n            object: newIntent.object || oldIntent.object,\n            target: newIntent.target || oldIntent.target,\n            scene: newIntent.scene || oldIntent.scene,\n            budget: newIntent.budget || oldIntent.budget,\n            time: newIntent.time || oldIntent.time\n        };\n    } else {\n        // 首次对话\n        intent = newIntent;\n\n[233 more lines in file. Use offset=285 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773382959268}}
{"type":"message","id":"ce3e0673","parentId":"8ddac4e5","timestamp":"2026-03-13T06:22:59.649Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The issue is in the merge logic - it always prefers old object if new object is null. But for vague keywords, we should NOT use the old object. Let me fix this:","thinkingSignature":"eb7bf5e104de0c2f1f3c3d8ff267046083fe9b3d6844a1e5572aabbff3ab74f9"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_awmwh0lnf7a3_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"newText":"async function handleChat(message, familyId, option = null) {\n    let intent = {};\n    \n    // 优先从消息中提取意图（每次都重新识别，保留最新信息）\n    const newIntent = processIntent(message || option);\n    \n    // 检查是否包含模糊词（礼物、东西等）\n    const vagueKeywords = [\"礼物\", \"东西\", \"物品\", \"物件\", \"想买\", \"买点什么\", \"买点\", \"看看\", \"推荐\"];\n    const hasVague = vagueKeywords.some(kw => (message || \"\").includes(kw));\n    \n    if (conversationState[familyId]) {\n        // 有历史上下文，合并新旧意图\n        const oldIntent = conversationState[familyId].intent || {};\n        \n        // 如果新消息包含模糊词，则不使用旧的object\n        const useOldObject = newIntent.object || (hasVague ? null : oldIntent.object);\n        \n        intent = {\n            intent_type: newIntent.intent_type || oldIntent.intent_type,\n            object: useOldObject,\n            target: newIntent.target || oldIntent.target,\n            scene: newIntent.scene || oldIntent.scene,\n            budget: newIntent.budget || oldIntent.budget,\n            time: newIntent.time || oldIntent.time\n        };\n    } else {\n        // 首次对话\n        intent = newIntent;","old_string":"async function handleChat(message, familyId, option = null) {\n    let intent = {};\n    \n    // 优先从消息中提取意图（每次都重新识别，保留最新信息）\n    const newIntent = processIntent(message || option);\n    \n    if (conversationState[familyId]) {\n        // 有历史上下文，合并新旧意图（取最新的非空值）\n        const oldIntent = conversationState[familyId].intent || {};\n        intent = {\n            i