{"type":"message","id":"3e0f2586","parentId":"86400d45","timestamp":"2026-03-13T06:25:32.745Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_7azzzelm06xr_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n------------------------------------------------------------\n2. 消费意图识别\n------------------------------------------------------------\n\n识别三个核心维度：\n\n1）意图阶段\n\nawareness      只是产生兴趣  \nconsideration  正在比较  \npurchase       准备购买  \n\n\n示例：\n\n想买个手机        → awareness  \n手机哪个好        → consideration  \n准备买 iPhone     → purchase  \n\n\n2）意图强度\n\nlow  \nmedium  \nhigh  \n\n示例：\n\n随便看看 → low  \n想买一个 → medium  \n准备今天买 → high  \n\n\n3）商品类别（17 类）\n\neducation\nappliance\nfood\ndaily\ndigital\nclothing\nentertainment\nhealth\nservice\ntravel\nfurniture\nbaby\nelderly\nsports\n\n[379 more lines in file. Use offset=123 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773383132743}}
{"type":"message","id":"84a5374c","parentId":"3e0f2586","timestamp":"2026-03-13T06:25:43.897Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我在第2节的末尾添加新的识别规则。","thinkingSignature":"6c68f85d4dee3a36726021bec913adb7ecce4f4cf2e5e5a88d92c148354d9d51"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_94f0g3rk3nsk_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"newText":"------------------------------------------------------------\n2. 消费意图识别\n------------------------------------------------------------\n\n识别三个核心维度：\n\n1）意图阶段\n\nawareness      只是产生兴趣  \nconsideration  正在比较  \npurchase       准备购买  \n\n\n示例：\n\n想买个手机        → awareness  \n手机哪个好        → consideration  \n准备买 iPhone     → purchase  \n\n\n2）意图强度\n\nlow  \nmedium  \nhigh  \n\n示例：\n\n随便看看 → low  \n想买一个 → medium  \n准备今天买 → high  \n\n\n3）商品类别（17 类）\n\neducation\nappliance\nfood\ndaily\ndigital\nclothing\nentertainment\nhealth\nservice\ntravel\nfurniture\nbaby\nelderly\nsports\nbeauty\npet\ncar\n\n\n**⚠️ 识别优化规则：**\n\n1. **模糊词处理**\n   - 以下词汇不应被识别为具体商品：\n     - 礼物、东西、物品、物件\n     - 想买、买点什么、买点\n     - 看看、推荐\n   - 遇到模糊词时，object 设为 null，继续追问\n\n2. **关键词优先级**\n   - 消费对象：孩子 > 父母 > 家庭 > 自己\n   - 避免\"自己\"优先级过高\n\n3. **场景词识别**\n   - \"开学了\" → 场景，不是商品\n   - \"坏了\" → 场景\n   - \"过年/春节\" → 节日场景","old_string":"------------------------------------------------------------\n2. 消费意图识别\n------------------------------------------------------------\n\n识别三个核心维度：\n\n1）意图阶段\n\nawareness      只是产生兴趣  \nconsideration  正在比较  \npurchase       准备购买  \n\n\n示例：\n\n想买个手机        → awareness  \n手机哪个好        → consideration  \n准备买 iPhone     → purchase  \n\n\n2）意图强度\n\nlow  \nmedium  \nhigh  \n\n示例：\n\n随便看看 → low  \n想买一个 → medium  \n准备今天买 → high  \n\n\n3）商品类别（17 类）\n\neducation\nappliance\nfood\ndaily\ndigital\nclothing\nentertainment\nhealth\nservice\ntravel\nfurniture\nbaby\nelderly\nsports","path":"/home/robot/.openclaw/workspace-family_consumption_intent/AGENTS.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage"