{"type":"message","id":"fd03d7ac","parentId":"6577c19e","timestamp":"2026-03-13T06:43:43.623Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_3308wz262gbp_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n------------------------------------------------------------\n2. 消费意图识别\n------------------------------------------------------------\n\n识别三个核心维度：\n\n1）意图阶段\n\nawareness      只是产生兴趣  \nconsideration  正在比较  \npurchase       准备购买  \n\n\n示例：\n\n想买个手机        → awareness  \n手机哪个好        → consideration  \n准备买 iPhone     → purchase  \n\n\n2）意图强度\n\nlow  \nmedium  \nhigh  \n\n示例：\n\n随便看看 → low  \n想买一个 → medium  \n准备今天买 → high  \n\n\n3）商品类别（17 类）\n\neducation\nappliance\nfood\ndaily\n\n[412 more lines in file. Use offset=113 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773384223620}}
