{"type":"message","id":"ed6f5da8","parentId":"3cc16d28","timestamp":"2026-03-13T06:49:19.501Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在更新 TOOLS.md","thinkingSignature":"b44b18e2926b0b3d6a4eff2db743eb0933f2c7f9d1ef5699ed93f15a45198255"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_0sh8ftut9znj_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# TOOLS.md - 工具配置\n\n_本工作空间使用的工具和服务_\n\n## API 服务\n\n- **服务:** family-sync-server.js\n- **端口:** 3847\n- **地址:** http://192.168.3.33:3847\n\n## 接口\n\n- POST /api/chat - 意图识别对话\n- GET /api/families - 获取家庭列表\n- GET /api/history - 获取消费历史\n\n## 家庭画像\n\n- **文件:** /home/robot/.openclaw/workspace/skills/family-consumption-intent/family_profile/family_profiles.json\n\n## 测试页面\n\n- test.html - 基础测试页面\n- test_v2.html - 飞书风格测试页面\n- 访问地址: http://192.168.3.33:8889/test_v2.html\n","path":"/home/robot/.openclaw/workspace-family_consumption_intent/TOOLS.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":139396,"output":233,"cacheRead":9179,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":148808,"cost":{"input":0.041818799999999996,"output":0.00027959999999999997,"cacheRead":0.00027537,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.04237376999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773384552023}}
