{"type":"message","id":"534b9d5a","parentId":"efcbc137","timestamp":"2026-03-13T08:18:21.844Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我需要更新 AGENTS.md，明确根据 userId 来确定加载哪个用户画像和 memory。","thinkingSignature":"3feec93c7d9b180802ddcf3f4f40ca237c77dee8b95e42a8877b507b732e022d"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_zx3llf9hfs0z_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"newText":"## ⚠️ 启动加载（每次必执行）\n\n**1. 根据 userId 加载对应配置**\n\n每次请求必须携带 userId 参数，根据 userId 确定：\n- 加载对应的家庭画像（USER_xxx.md）\n- 加载对应的用户记忆（memory/xxx.md）\n\n```\n用户ID → USER_xxx.md + memory/xxx.md\n```\n\n**2. 用户画像加载规则**\n- 优先加载 USER_{userId}.md\n- 如果不存在，加载默认的 USER.md\n- 读取 income_level、consume_style、members 等信息\n- 用于预算预测和个性化推荐\n\n**3. 用户记忆加载规则**\n- 优先加载 memory/{userId}.md\n- 如果不存在，创建新记忆文件\n- 加载消费历史、近期需求、偏好习惯\n- 用于上下文理解和连续对话","old_string":"## ⚠️ 启动加载（每次必执行）\n\n**1. 加载用户画像**\n- 读取 USER.md 文件中的 JSON 块\n- 获取 income_level、consume_style、members 等信息\n- 用于预算预测和个性化推荐\n\n**2. 加载用户记忆**\n- 从 memory/ 目录加载历史对话记录\n- 消费历史、近期需求、偏好习惯\n- 用于上下文理解和连续对话","path":"/home/robot/.openclaw/workspace-family_consumption_intent/AGENTS.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":163518,"output":341,"cacheRead":9179,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":173038,"cost":{"input":0.0490554,"output":0.00040919999999999997,"cacheRead":0.00027537,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.049739969999999994}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773389892021}}
