{"type":"compaction","id":"77408f3b","parentId":"9e98d1df","timestamp":"2026-03-13T08:34:21.218Z","summary":"## Decisions\n- **Question-only mode implemented**: Added `hide_details: true` to API response when `is_complete: false`, so frontend can conditionally hide identification results, slot info, and recommendations\n- **Recommendations cleared when incomplete**: Set `recommendations: []` when incomplete to prevent showing stale data\n- **Family profile stored in USER.md**: Loaded at server startup with JSON block for easier management\n- **Vague keywords (礼物,东西,物品,物件,看看,推荐)**: Trigger follow-up questions\n- **consume_style \"大方\"**: Maps to budget 5000-8000\n\n## Open TODOs\n- Fix duplicate \"孩子\" key in family-sync-server.js targetKeywords\n- Verify test page is working properly for user testing\n- Fix: single character misrecognition (茶 → target:孩子)\n- Fix: English product recognition (iPhone, MacBook)\n- Fix: 六一儿童节 scene recognition (日常 → 节日)\n- Re-run 100 test cases with same inputs, output results\n\n## Constraints/Rules\n1. target + object are the ONLY required fields\n2. Ask only one question at a time\n3. Scene and budget auto-predicted from family profile (consumption_style)\n4. No specific product recommendations - only purchasing advice\n5. When incomplete: only ask questions, don't display partial identification\n6. API returns `hide_details: true` when incomplete to signal frontend to only show question\n\n## Pending user asks\n- \"把问题整理优化agents文件，并基于相同的测试用例，二次测试，输出测试结果\" - Organize problems in AGENTS, re-test with same test cases, output results\n- ✅ **RESOLVED**: API now returns `hide_details: true` when incomplete, frontend should only display `next_question`\n\n## Exact identifiers\n- Workspace: `/home/robot/.openclaw/workspace-family_consumption_intent/`\n- Server file: `/home/robot/.openclaw/workspace/family-sync-server.js`\n- API URL: `http://127.0.0.1:3847/api/chat`\n- Test HTML files: `test.html`, `test_v2.html`\n- User ID: `ou_d0f1627a7a508d84d750914fbb6a2fc2` (吴海超)\n- Family ID: `default`\n- Test ports: 3847 (API), 8888/8889/8890 (HTTP server)\n- Test page: `http://192.168.3.33:8889/test_v2.html`\n- Family profile: `/home/robot/.openclaw/workspace-family_consumption_intent/USER.md`\n- AGENTS.md: `/home/robot/.openclaw/workspace-family_consumption_intent/AGENTS.md`\n- Test file: `/home/robot/.openclaw/workspace-family_consumption_intent/test_cases_1000.md`\n- Conversation IDs: om_x100b540c717888a0c3e23e01f2153fd, om_x100b540c0ecc6d38c4cfd0b0187f416, om_x100b540e70801ca8c32d92b250edf49, om_x100b540e717dec80c4282b4b367c244\n- Message IDs: om_x100b540e0c557084c3f2ea485d9d053, om_x100b540e07c3acbcc4f647a9ea244d1\n- Members: [\"爸爸\", \"妈妈\", \"孩子\"]\n- Baby category keywords added: 婴儿车, 遛娃神器, 腰凳, 背带, 尿不湿, 婴儿床, 儿童床, 儿童椅, 学习桌, 护眼灯, 台灯, 早教机, 点读机, 滑板车, 轮滑鞋\n- Scene keywords: 节日: [节日, 春节, 中秋, 国庆, 生日, 过年, 六一, 儿童节, 情人节, 七夕, 母亲节, 父亲节], 促销: [促销, 打折, 优惠, 双11, 618]\n\n## Goal\n1. Develop and test a family consumption intent recognition system\n2. Create and run 1000 test cases, save results\n3. Optimize AGENTS.md with identified problems and fixes, then re-test\n4. Fix remaining issues: compound words (婴儿车, 遛娃神器), scene recognition (过年, 双11, 六一儿童节), vague keyword handling\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Use AGENTS.md as the main specification document\n- Store family profile in USER.md for easy loading\n- Maintain context memory for multi-turn conversations\n- Use vague keywords (礼物, 东西) to trigger follow-up questions\n- Required fields: target (消费对象) + object (商品)\n- Vague words trigger follow-up questions\n- Scene and budget auto-predicted from family profile\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] Created AGENTS.md with intent recognition rules and optimization guidelines\n- [x] Created test case files (test_cases.md, test_cases_100.md, test_cases_1000.md)\n- [x] Updated identity files: IDENTITY.md, USER.md, TOOLS.md, SOUL.md\n- [x] Optimized recognition algorithm: vague keywords handling, context memory\n- [x] Moved family profile storage from JSON to USER.md\n- [x] Identified key problems in testing\n- [x] Updated AGENTS.md with problem records\n- [x] Fixed compound word recognition (婴儿车, 遛娃神器) - added to \"baby\" category\n- [x] Fixed scene keyword 过年 → scene:节日\n- [x] Fixed scene keyword 双11 → scene:促销\n- [x] Fixed vague keyword 礼物 → triggers follow-up question \"想买什么商品？\"\n- [x] Conducted second round testing after AGENTS.md optimization\n- [x] Updated AGENTS.md with question-only rule for incomplete intent\n- [x] Added `hide_details` flag to API response (line ~361 in family-sync-server.js)\n- [x] Tested API behavior: incomplete=\"买手机\" → hide_details=true; complete=\"给孩子买手机\" → hide_details=false\n- [x] User tested: \"我想给孩子买个礼物\" → detected target=孩子, missing object → responded with question only\n- [x] User tested: \"电脑\" → detected object=电脑, missing target → responded with question only\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] Verify frontend test page properly uses `hide_details` flag to hide intent details\n- [ ] Further optimize remaining scene recognition issues (六一儿童节 → 节日)\n- [ ] Fix single character misrecognition (茶 → target:孩子)\n\n### Blocked\n- 六一儿童节 still shows scene:日常 instead of 节日\n- Some context residue causing incorrect target:孩子 in some cases\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **Question-only mode implemented**: Added `hide_details: true` to API response when `is_complete: false`, so frontend can conditionally hide identification results, slot info, and recommendations\n- **Recommendations cleared when incomplete**: Set `recommendations: []` when incomplete to prevent showing stale data\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Fix 六一儿童节 scene recognition (should be 节日 not 日常)\n2. Fix single character recognition (茶叶 → target should be None)\n3. Fix English product recognition (iPhone, MacBook)\n4. Verify all test cases pass after fixes\n5. Verify test_v2.html properly handles `hide_details` flag (only shows next_question when true)\n6. Continue testing full flow: user provides both target and object → should show full analysis\n\n## Critical Context\n- Server runs on port 3847\n- Test page: http://192.168.3.33:8889/test_v2.html\n- Family profile in USER.md with members: [\"爸爸\", \"妈妈\", \"孩子\"]\n- Server: /home/robot/.openclaw/workspace/family-sync-server.js\n- API endpoint: http://127.0.0.1:3847/api/chat\n- User is actively testing the conversation flow via the API\n- Server restarted successfully on port 3847\n- New behavior confirmed working: incomplete requests only return `next_question`, complete requests return full data with `hide_details: false`\n\n---\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n## Goal\nOptimize the AGENTS.md file for a \"家庭消费意图识别助手\" (Family Consumption Intent Recognition Assistant). The user wants to improve the agent's documentation.\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- (none explicitly mentioned)\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- Started analysis of AGENTS.md file structure\n- Examined file length (561 lines)\n- Identified key sections: Core workflow, Monitor family conversation, Consumption intent recognition, Maintain family profile, Consumption intent recording\n\n### In Progress\n- Reading and analyzing AGENTS.md content to identify optimization opportunities\n\n### Blocked\n- None - analysis phase ongoing\n\n## Key Decisions\n- None yet - still in initial analysis phase\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Complete reading of AGENTS.md content\n2. Identify areas for improvement in intent detection, slot filling, and other workflows\n3. Implement optimizations to the AGENTS.md documentation\n\n## Critical Context\n- File path: /home/robot/.openclaw/workspace-family_consumption_intent/AGENTS.md\n- Agent is designed to: identify consumption needs, fill missing information, record consumption history, provide personalized suggestions\n- Current workflow: User message → Intent detection → Slot checking → Recommendation system or Auto-ask follow-ups\n- Contains recognition rules for fuzzy words, keyword priorities, scene word recognition, product keyword expan