{"type":"message","id":"445720fd","parentId":"2d353465","timestamp":"2026-03-13T08:43:08.814Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now all users have different budgets based on their consume_style. Let me update the memory files with the test results.","thinkingSignature":"6926765970c6832d18a9e1968c82af90264e93585c9f1ac8da1d8e160734da9c"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_i27zrx169qry_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 << 'EOF'\nimport requests\nimport json\n\ncases = [\"给孩子买手机\",\"给父母买保健品\",\"买空调\",\"过年买年货\",\"中秋节买月饼\",\"六一儿童节给孩子买礼物\",\"生日买蛋糕\",\"开学了买书包\",\"坏了想换个冰箱\",\"换季买衣服\"]\nusers = [\"wuhaichao\",\"lihua\",\"zhangsan\",\"wangmei\",\"liuxiao\",\"chenyun\",\"zhaolei\",\"sunli\",\"yangfan\",\"zhoujing\"]\nstyle_map = {\"wuhaichao\":\"大方\",\"lihua\":\"理性\",\"zhangsan\":\"大方\",\"wangmei\":\"节俭\",\"liuxiao\":\"适度\",\"chenyun\":\"理性\",\"zhaolei\":\"大方\",\"sunli\":\"节俭\",\"yangfan\":\"奢侈\",\"zhoujing\":\"理性\"}\n\nfor uid in users:\n    complete = 0\n    budgets = []\n    for msg in cases:\n        try:\n            r = requests.post(\"http://127.0.0.1:3847/api/chat\", json={\"message\":msg,\"userId\":uid}, timeout=3)\n            d = r.json()\n            if d.get(\"is_complete\"):\n                complete += 1\n                budgets.append(d.get(\"intent\",{}).get(\"budget\",\"-\"))\n            else:\n                budgets.append(\"追问\")\n        except:\n            budgets.append(\"错误\")\n    \n    content = f\"\"\"# 用户记忆 - {uid}\n\n## 家庭画像\n- consume_style: {style_map.get(uid)}\n- income_level: 中\n\n## 测试结果\n- 测试用例: 10句\n- 完整识别: {complete}/10\n\n## 预算预测\n- 手机: {budgets[0]}\n- 空调: {budgets[2]}\n- 冰箱: {budgets[8]}\n\n## 详细结果\n| 用例 | 结果 |\n|------|------|\n| 给孩子买手机 | {budgets[0]} |\n| 买空调 | {budgets[2]} |\n| 坏了想换个冰箱 | {budgets[8]} |\n\"\"\"\n    with open(f\"/home/robot/.openclaw/workspace-family_consumption_intent/memory/{uid}.md\", \"w\") as f:\n        f.write(content)\n\nprint(\"记忆文件已更新！\")\nEOF","timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":49268,"output":533,"cacheRead":9179,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":58980,"cost":{"input":0.014780399999999999,"output":0.0006395999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00027537,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01569537}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773391375193}}
