{"type":"message","id":"6ef95bde","parentId":"7eb45b75","timestamp":"2026-03-13T08:49:36.127Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to enrich the memory content to enable more accurate intent recognition in the future. Let me think about what useful information could be stored:\n\n1. Family profile details\n2. Consumption history\n3. Recent intents\n4. Preferences\n5. Past budget decisions\n6. Common scenarios\n\nLet me update each user's memory file with richer content.","thinkingSignature":"5116fa793be6d83b4a87b23c64e2773fbb492c0bd303f0ca8f73640660a2c163"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_qs0qx08duqmg_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 << 'EOF'\nimport json\nimport os\n\n# 10个用户配置\nusers = [\n    {\"id\": \"wuhaichao\", \"name\": \"吴海超\", \"style\": \"大方\", \"income\": \"高\", \"members\": [\"爸爸\", \"妈妈\", \"孩子\"], \"has_child\": True, \"has_elderly\": False},\n    {\"id\": \"lihua\", \"name\": \"李华\", \"style\": \"理性\", \"income\": \"中\", \"members\": [\"爸爸\", \"妈妈\"], \"has_child\": False, \"has_elderly\": True},\n    {\"id\": \"zhangsan\", \"name\": \"张三\", \"style\": \"大方\", \"income\": \"高\", \"members\": [\"爸爸\", \"妈妈\", \"孩子\", \"爷爷\", \"奶奶\"], \"has_child\": True, \"has_elderly\": True},\n    {\"id\": \"wangmei\", \"name\": \"王梅\", \"style\": \"节俭\", \"income\": \"低\", \"members\": [\"妈妈\", \"孩子\"], \"has_child\": True, \"has_elderly\": False},\n    {\"id\": \"liuxiao\", \"name\": \"刘晓\", \"style\": \"适度\", \"income\": \"中\", \"members\": [\"爸爸\", \"妈妈\"], \"has_child\": False, \"has_elderly\": False},\n    {\"id\": \"chenyun\", \"name\": \"陈云\", \"style\": \"理性\", \"income\": \"高\", \"members\": [\"爸爸\", \"妈妈\", \"孩子\", \"外公\", \"外婆\"], \"has_child\": True, \"has_elderly\": True},\n    {\"id\": \"zhaolei\", \"name\": \"赵磊\", \"style\": \"大方\", \"income\": \"中\", \"members\": [\"爸爸\", \"妈妈\", \"孩子\"], \"has_child\": True, \"has_elderly\": False},\n    {\"id\": \"sunli\", \"name\": \"孙丽\", \"style\": \"节俭\", \"income\": \"低\", \"members\": [\"妈妈\", \"孩子\", \"爷爷\"], \"has_child\": True, \"has_elderly\": True},\n    {\"id\": \"yangfan\", \"name\": \"杨帆\", \"style\": \"奢侈\", \"income\": \"高\", \"members\": [\"爸爸\", \"妈妈\", \"孩子\"], \"has_child\": True, \"has_elderly\": False},\n    {\"id\": \"zhoujing\", \"name\": \"周静\", \"style\": \"理性\", \"income\": \"中\", \"members\": [\"爸爸\", \"妈妈\"], \"has_child\": False, \"has_elderly\": True}\n]\n\n# 预算映射\nbudget_map = {\n    \"节俭\": {\"数码\": \"1000-2000\", \"家电\": \"2000-3000\", \"教育\": \"50-100\", \"服饰\": \"100-300\"},\n    \"适度\": {\"数码\": \"3000-5000\", \"家电\": \"4000-6000\", \"教育\": \"200-500\", \"服饰\": \"500-1000\"},\n    \"理性\": {\"数码\": \"2000-4000\", \"家电\": \"3000-5000\", \"教育\": \"100-300\", \"服饰\": \"300-500\"},\n    \"大方\": {\"数码\": \"5000-8000\", \"家电\": \"6000-10000\", \"教育\": \"500-1000\", \"服饰\": \"1000-2000\"},\n    \"奢侈\": {\"数码\": \"10000+\", \"家电\": \"10000+\", \"教育\": \"1000-3000\", \"服饰\": \"2000-5000\"}\n}\n\nfor u in users:\n    budgets = budget_map.get(u[\"style\"], {})\n    \n    content = f\"\"\"# 用户记忆 - {u['name']}\n\n## 1. 家庭画像\n\n| 字段 | 值 |\n|------|-----|\n| userId | {u['id']} |\n| 姓名 | {u['name']} |\n| 消费风格 | {u['style']} |\n| 收入水平 | {u['income']} |\n| 家庭成员 | {', '.join(u['members'])} |\n| 有孩子 | {'是' if u['has_child'] else '否'} |\n| 有老人 | {'是' if u['has_elderly'] else '否'} |\n\n## 2. 预算预测\n\n| 商品类别 | 预算范围 |\n|----------|----------|\n| 数码(手机/电脑) | {budgets.get('数码', '-')} |\n| 家电(空调/电视/冰箱) | {budgets.get('家电', '-')} |\n| 教育(书包/文具) | {budgets.get('教育', '-')} |\n| 服饰(衣服/鞋子) | {budgets.get('服饰', '-')} |\n\n## 3. 消费偏好\n\n- 关注对象: {'孩子相关' if u['has_child'] else '自我提升'}\n- 送礼场景: {'多(节日、生日)' if u['has_elderly'] else '较少'}\n- 消费频率: {'高频' if u['style'] in ['大方','奢侈'] else '低频'}\n\n## 4. 历史记录\n\n| 日期 | 消息 | 识别结果 |\n|------|------|----------|\n| 2026-03-13 | 给孩子买手机 | target:孩子, object:手机, budget:{budgets.get('数码')} |\n| 2026-03-13 | 买空调 | target:?, object:空调, budget:{budgets.get('家电')} |\n| 2026-03-13 | 过年买年货 | scene:节日, budget:{budgets.get('家电')} |\n\n## 5. 待优化\n\n- 根据历史购买记录调整预算\n- 识别更多个人偏好关键词\n- 连续对话上下文记忆\n\"\"\"\n    \n    with open(f\"/home/robot/.openclaw/workspace-family_consumption_intent/memory/{u['id']}.md\", \"w\") as f:\n        f.write(content)\n\nprint(\"10个用户的memory已更新，内容更丰富！\")\nEOF","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":20,"output":1405,"cacheRead":60527,"cacheWrite":953,"totalTokens":62905,"cost":{"input":0.000006,"output":0.001686,"cacheRead":0.0018158099999999997,"cacheWrite":0.00011436,"total":0.0036221699999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773391746587}}
