{"type":"message","id":"bb2ea189","parentId":"b8cfef46","timestamp":"2026-03-13T08:51:53.932Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to think about how to further improve and enrich the memory content for better intent recognition. Let me think about what else could be useful:\n\n1. **Consumption patterns** - what products has the user bought before?\n2. **Price sensitivity** - how price-sensitive is the user?\n3. **Shopping channels** - where do they usually buy (online, offline)?\n4. **Brand preferences** - any known brand preferences?\n5. **Time patterns** - when do they usually make purchases (seasonal, special dates)?\n6. **Decision factors** - what matters most (price, quality, brand, reviews)?\n7. **Rejected suggestions** - what have they rejected before?\n8. **Family events** - birthdays, anniversaries coming up\n9. **Emergency replacements** - things that broke and needed immediate replacement\n10. **Gift giving history** - who do they usually buy gifts for?\n\nLet me create a more comprehensive memory structure.","thinkingSignature":"b10cd30dd49c151feea6bfae4e557627c446fa9d1be6cda2838628d586b6df3f"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_b8gaxlsq290m_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 << 'EOF'\nimport json\nimport os\n\n# 10个用户配置 - 更丰富\nusers = [\n    {\"id\": \"wuhaichao\", \"name\": \"吴海超\", \"style\": \"大方\", \"income\": \"高\", \"members\": [\"爸爸\", \"妈妈\", \"孩子\"], \"has_child\": True, \"has_elderly\": False, \"channels\": [\"京东\", \"天猫\"], \"brands\": [\"苹果\", \"华为\"], \"events\": [\"六一儿童节\", \"生日\"]},\n    {\"id\": \"lihua\", \"name\": \"李华\", \"style\": \"理性\", \"income\": \"中\", \"members\": [\"爸爸\", \"妈妈\"], \"has_child\": False, \"has_elderly\": True, \"channels\": [\"京东\", \"拼多多\"], \"brands\": [\"小米\", \"美的\"], \"events\": [\"春节\", \"中秋节\"]},\n    {\"id\": \"zhangsan\", \"name\": \"张三\", \"style\": \"大方\", \"income\": \"高\", \"members\": [\"爸爸\", \"妈妈\", \"孩子\", \"爷爷\", \"奶奶\"], \"has_child\": True, \"has_elderly\": True, \"channels\": [\"京东\", \"线下门店\"], \"brands\": [\"苹果\", \"戴森\"], \"events\": [\"春节\", \"端午\", \"中秋节\", \"重阳节\"]},\n    {\"id\": \"wangmei\", \"name\": \"王梅\", \"style\": \"节俭\", \"income\": \"低\", \"members\": [\"妈妈\", \"孩子\"], \"has_child\": True, \"has_elderly\": False, \"channels\": [\"拼多多\", \"淘宝\"], \"brands\": [\"小米\", \"荣耀\"], \"events\": [\"生日\", \"六一儿童节\"]},\n    {\"id\": \"liuxiao\", \"name\": \"刘晓\", \"style\": \"适度\", \"income\": \"中\", \"members\": [\"爸爸\", \"妈妈\"], \"has_child\": False, \"has_elderly\": False, \"channels\": [\"天猫\", \"京东\"], \"brands\": [\"苹果\", \"戴森\"], \"events\": [\"周年纪念日\"]},\n    {\"id\": \"chenyun\", \"name\": \"陈云\", \"style\": \"理性\", \"income\": \"高\", \"members\": [\"爸爸\", \"妈妈\", \"孩子\", \"外公\", \"外婆\"], \"has_child\": True, \"has_elderly\": True, \"channels\": [\"京东\", \"天猫\"], \"brands\": [\"华为\", \"美的\"], \"events\": [\"春节\", \"中秋节\", \"母亲节\", \"父亲节\"]},\n    {\"id\": \"zhaolei\", \"name\": \"赵磊\", \"style\": \"大方\", \"income\": \"中\", \"members\": [\"爸爸\", \"妈妈\", \"孩子\"], \"has_child\": True, \"has_elderly\": False, \"channels\": [\"京东\", \"天猫\"], \"brands\": [\"苹果\", \"索尼\"], \"events\": [\"生日\", \"六一儿童节\"]},\n    {\"id\": \"sunli\", \"name\": \"孙丽\", \"style\": \"节俭\", \"income\": \"低\", \"members\": [\"妈妈\", \"孩子\", \"爷爷\"], \"has_child\": True, \"has_elderly\": True, \"channels\": [\"拼多多\", \"淘宝\"], \"brands\": [\"小米\"], \"events\": [\"春节\", \"生日\"]},\n    {\"id\": \"yangfan\", \"name\": \"杨帆\", \"style\": \"奢侈\", \"income\": \"高\", \"members\": [\"爸爸\", \"妈妈\", \"孩子\"], \"has_child\": True, \"has_elderly\": False, \"channels\": [\"线下门店\", \"京东\"], \"brands\": [\"苹果\", \"戴森\", \"B&O\"], \"events\": [\"生日\", \"纪念日\"]},\n    {\"id\": \"zhoujing\", \"name\": \"周静\", \"style\": \"理性\", \"income\": \"中\", \"members\": [\"爸爸\", \"妈妈\"], \"has_child\": False, \"has_elderly\": True, \"channels\": [\"京东\", \"天猫\"], \"brands\": [\"小米\", \"美的\"], \"events\": [\"春节\", \"中秋节\", \"母亲节\"]}\n]\n\n# 预算映射\nbudget_map = {\n    \"节俭\": {\"数码\": \"1000-2000\", \"家电\": \"2000-3000\", \"教育\": \"50-100\", \"服饰\": \"100-300\", \"美妆\": \"100-200\"},\n    \"适度\": {\"数码\": \"3000-5000\", \"家电\": \"4000-6000\", \"教育\": \"200-500\", \"服饰\": \"500-1000\", \"美妆\": \"300-500\"},\n    \"理性\": {\"数码\": \"2000-4000\", \"家电\": \"3000-5000\", \"教育\": \"100-300\", \"服饰\": \"300-500\", \"美妆\": \"200-400\"},\n    \"大方\": {\"数码\": \"5000-8000\", \"家电\": \"6000-10000\", \"教育\": \"500-1000\", \"服饰\": \"1000-2000\", \"美妆\": \"500-1000\"},\n    \"奢侈\": {\"数码\": \"10000+\", \"家电\": \"10000+\", \"教育\": \"1000-3000\", \"服饰\": \"2000-5000\", \"美妆\": \"1000-3000\"}\n}\n\nfor u in users:\n    budgets = budget_map.get(u[\"style\"], {})\n    \n    # 根据消费风格生成偏好描述\n    price_sens = \"低\" if u[\"style\"] in [\"节俭\",\"理性\"] else (\"中\" if u[\"style\"] == \"适度\" else \"高\")\n    quality = \"高\" if u[\"style\"] in [\"理性\",\"奢侈\",\"大方\"] else \"实用\"\n    \n    content = f\"\"\"# 用户记忆 - {u['name']}\n\n## 1. 家庭画像\n\n| 字段 | 值 |\n|------|-----|\n| userId | {u['id']} |\n| 姓名 | {u['name']} |\n| 消费风格 | {u['style']} |\n| 收入水平 | {u['income']} |\n| 家庭成员 | {', '.join(u['members'])} |\n| 有孩子 | {'是' if u['has_child'] else '否'} |\n| 有老人 | {'是' if u['has_elderly'] else '否'} |\n\n## 2. 预算预测\n\n| 商品类别 | 预算范围 |\n|----------|----------|\n| 数码(手机/电脑) | {budgets.get('数码', '-')} |\n| 家电(空调/电视/冰箱) | {budgets.get('家电', '-')} |\n| 教育(书包/文具) | {budgets.get('教育', '-')} |\n| 服饰(衣服/鞋子) | {budgets.get('服饰', '-')} |\n| 美妆(化妆品/护肤品) | {budgets.get('美妆', '-')} |\n\n## 3. 消费偏好\n\n### 购物渠道\n- 主要: {', '.join(u['channels'])}\n\n### 品牌偏好\n- 偏好品牌: {', '.join(u['brands'])}\n- 品牌价位: {'高端' if u['style'] == '奢侈' else ('中高端' if u['style'] == '大方' else '性价比')}\n\n### 决策因素\n- 价格敏感度: {price_sens} (根据消费风格)\n- 质量要求: {quality}\n- 购物频率: {'高频' if u['style'] in ['大方','奢侈'] else '理性'}\n\n## 4. 重要节日\n\n| 节日 | 送礼对象 |\n|------|----------|\n{chr(10).join([f\"| {e} | {'孩子/家人' if u['has_child'] else '父母'} |\" for e in u['events']])}\n\n## 5. 历史记录\n\n| 日期 | 消息 | 识别结果 |\n|------|------|----------|\n| 2026-03-13 | 给孩子买手机 | target:孩子, object:手机, budget:{budgets.get('数码')} |\n| 2026-03-13 | 买空调 | target:?, object:空调, budget:{budgets.get('家电')} |\n| 2026-03-13 | 过年买年货 | scene:节日, budget:{budgets.get('家电')} |\n\n## 6. 意图识别策略\n\n- **target预测**: {'优先识别孩子' if u['has_child'] else '优先识别自己'}\n- **scene预测**: {'春节/中秋/重阳等大家庭节日' if u['has_elderly'] else ('六一/生日等孩子节日' if u['has_child'] else '日常')}\n- **budget预测**: 根据consume_style自动匹配\n- **商品推荐**: {'推荐高性价比' if u['style'] == '节俭' else ('推荐品牌旗舰' if u['style'] == '奢侈' else '推荐适中')}\n\n## 7. 待优化\n\n- [ ] 根据实际购买记录更新历史\n- [ ] 记录被拒绝的推荐\n- [ ] 补充实际使用的购物渠道\n- [ ] 添加品牌黑名单\n\"\"\"\n    \n    with open(f\"/home/robot/.openclaw/workspace-family_consumption_intent/memory/{u['id']}.md\", \"w\") as f:\n        f.write(content)\n\nprint(\"✅ 10个用户的memory已更新，内容更完善！\")\nEOF","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":20,"output":2264,"cacheRead":61325,"cacheWrite":2296,"totalTokens":65905,"cost":{"input":0.000006,"output":0.0027167999999999997,"cacheRead":0.0018397499999999998,"cacheWrite":0.00027551999999999996,"total":0.004838069999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773391860661}}
