{"type":"message","id":"9d94766c","parentId":"8a4066b0","timestamp":"2026-03-13T09:01:26.150Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see, this v1.0.2 has a proper git repo structure. Let me create a new folder with similar structure and proper git init.","thinkingSignature":"c36ba50be1fffa6e1ee90e649da89ece6d766fc7d82b679d1842bc11b4ed29a9"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_mnc4lqtt6md6_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mkdir -p /home/robot/.openclaw/workspace/git/family-intent-recognition-v2.0\n\n# 复制核心文件\ncp /home/robot/.openclaw/workspace/family-sync-server.js /home/robot/.openclaw/workspace/git/family-intent-recognition-v2.0/\ncp /home/robot/.openclaw/workspace-family_consumption_intent/AGENTS.md /home/robot/.openclaw/workspace/git/family-intent-recognition-v2.0/\ncp /home/robot/.openclaw/workspace-family_consumption_intent/USER.md /home/robot/.openclaw/workspace/git/family-intent-recognition-v2.0/\ncp /home/robot/.openclaw/workspace-family_consumption_intent/test.html /home/robot/.openclaw/workspace/git/family-intent-recognition-v2.0/\n\n# 复制文件夹\ncp -r /home/robot/.openclaw/workspace-family_consumption_intent/USER /home/robot/.openclaw/workspace/git/family-intent-recognition-v2.0/\ncp -r /home/robot/.openclaw/workspace-family_consumption_intent/memory /home/robot/.openclaw/workspace/git/family-intent-recognition-v2.0/\n\n# 创建更完善的README\ncat > /home/robot/.openclaw/workspace/git/family-intent-recognition-v2.0/README.md << 'EOF'\n# 家庭消费意图识别助手\n\n智能识别家庭成员的消费意图，提供个性化选购建议。\n\n## 功能特性\n\n- 🎯 意图识别 - 识别消费对象(target)和商品(object)\n- 💰 预算预测 - 根据消费风格自动匹配预算\n- 💬 智能追问 - 信息不完整时主动询问\n- 👨‍👩‍👧‍👦 多用户支持 - 10种不同消费风格\n- 📝 历史记忆 - 记录用户偏好和历史记录\n\n## 快速开始\n\n### 安装依赖\n```bash\nnpm install express body-parser cors\n```\n\n### 启动服务\n```bash\nnode family-sync-server.js\n```\n\n### 测试\n```bash\n# 打开浏览器访问 test.html\n# 或使用 curl 测试\ncurl -X POST http://localhost:3847/api/chat \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"message\":\"给孩子买手机\",\"userId\":\"wuhaichao\"}'\n```\n\n## 用户配置\n\n| userId | 消费风格 | 收入 | 手机预算 |\n|--------|----------|------|----------|\n| wuhaichao | 大方 | 高 | 5000-8000 |\n| lihua | 理性 | 中 | 2000-4000 |\n| zhangsan | 大方 | 高 | 5000-8000 |\n| wangmei | 节俭 | 低 | 1000-2000 |\n| liuxiao | 适度 | 中 | 3000-5000 |\n| chenyun | 理性 | 高 | 2000-4000 |\n| zhaolei | 大方 | 中 | 5000-8000 |\n| sunli | 节俭 | 低 | 1000-2000 |\n| yangfan | 奢侈 | 高 | 10000+ |\n| zhoujing | 理性 | 中 | 2000-4000 |\n\n## API 说明\n\n### 请求\n```json\n{\n  \"message\": \"给孩子买手机\",\n  \"userId\": \"wuhaichao\"\n}\n```\n\n### 响应\n```json\n{\n  \"intent\": {\n    \"target\": \"孩子\",\n    \"object\": \"手机\",\n    \"intent_type\": \"digital\",\n    \"budget\": \"5000-8000\",\n    \"is_complete\": true\n  },\n  \"recommendations\": [...]\n}\n```\n\n## 文件结构\n\n```\nfamily-intent-recognition-v2.0/\n├── family-sync-server.js   # 服务端\n├── AGENTS.md              # 核心规则\n├── USER.md                # 默认用户配置\n├── test.html              # 测试页面\n├── USER/                   # 10个用户配置\n│   ├── USER_wuhaichao.md\n│   └── ...\n└── memory/                 # 用户记忆\n    ├── wuhaichao.md\n    └── ...\n```\n\n## 版本\n\nv2.0 - 多用户支持版本\nEOF\n\n# 初始化git\ncd /home/robot/.openclaw/workspace/git/family-intent-recognition-v2.0\ngit init\ngit add .\ngit commit -m \"v2.0: 家庭消费意图识别助手 - 多用户版本\"\n\necho \"=== v2.0 打包完成 ===\"\nls -la"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":73986,"output":1037,"cacheRead":9179,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":84202,"cost":{"input":0.022195799999999998,"output":0.0012443999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00027537,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02371557}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773392446648}}
