{"type":"message","id":"07515b74","parentId":"34547576","timestamp":"2026-03-13T09:17:55.292Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to rewrite the README. Let me create a cleaner, more concise README for the intent-agent.","thinkingSignature":"8cbdbf54ab6cc304de2e21cbf5e990061f5eaf8c152d343f4117fed7cbd58098"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_01pgnm55toxw_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat > /home/robot/.openclaw/workspace-family_consumption_intent/git/intent-agent/README.md << 'EOF'\n# Intent Agent - 家庭消费意图识别助手\n\n智能识别家庭成员的消费意图，提供个性化选购建议。\n\n## 功能\n\n- 🎯 意图识别 - 识别消费对象(target)和商品(object)\n- 💰 预算预测 - 根据消费风格自动匹配预算\n- 💬 智能追问 - 信息不完整时主动询问\n- 👨‍👩‍👧‍👦 多用户支持 - 10种不同消费风格\n- 📝 历史记忆 - 记录用户偏好\n\n## 快速开始\n\n```bash\n# 启动服务\ncd workspace\nnode family-sync-server.js\n```\n\n服务将在 http://localhost:3847 启动\n\n## API\n\n```bash\n# 测试\ncurl -X POST http://localhost:3847/api/chat \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"message\":\"给孩子买手机\",\"userId\":\"wuhaichao\"}'\n```\n\n## 用户配置\n\n| userId | 消费风格 | 手机预算 |\n|--------|----------|----------|\n| wuhaichao | 大方 | 5000-8000 |\n| lihua | 理性 | 2000-4000 |\n| zhangsan | 大方 | 5000-8000 |\n| wangmei | 节俭 | 1000-2000 |\n| liuxiao | 适度 | 3000-5000 |\n| chenyun | 理性 | 2000-4000 |\n| zhaolei | 大方 | 5000-8000 |\n| sunli | 节俭 | 1000-2000 |\n| yangfan | 奢侈 | 10000+ |\n| zhoujing | 理性 | 2000-4000 |\n\n## 文件结构\n\n```\nintent-agent/\n├── workspace/               # 工作目录\n│   ├── AGENTS.md         # 核心规则\n│   ├── USER/             # 用户配置\n│   └── memory/           # 用户记忆\n├── skills/               # 技能模块\n├── agent-config/         # 代理配置\n└── config/               # 配置文件\n```\n\n## 响应示例\n\n**完整识别：**\n```json\n{\n  \"intent\": {\n    \"target\": \"孩子\",\n    \"object\": \"手机\",\n    \"budget\": \"5000-8000\",\n    \"is_complete\": true\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**需要追问：**\n```json\n{\n  \"intent\": {\"is_complete\": false},\n  \"next_question\": \"想买什么商品？\"\n}\n```\n\n## License\n\nMIT\nEOF\n\necho \"README 已更新\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":20,"output":611,"cacheRead":105478,"cacheWrite":382,"totalTokens":106491,"cost":{"input":0.000006,"output":0.0007331999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00316434,"cacheWrite":0.000045839999999999995,"total":0.00394938}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773393453644}}
