{"type":"message","id":"19ab19e2","parentId":"4022f03d","timestamp":"2026-03-13T09:19:44.211Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我明白了。用户通过飞书进行测试。让我更新 README 包含飞书配置方式。","thinkingSignature":"e7f79edbbca29458e42ddb9ca4cc2bdff29d3edf794ee7fe67b85f411f235744"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_uhz5o1kh0z70_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat > /home/robot/.openclaw/workspace-family_consumption_intent/git/intent-agent/README.md << 'EOF'\n# Intent Agent - 家庭消费意图识别助手\n\n智能识别家庭成员的消费意图，提供个性化选购建议。\n\n## 功能\n\n- 🎯 意图识别 - 识别消费对象(target)和商品(object)\n- 💰 预算预测 - 根据消费风格自动匹配预算\n- 💬 智能追问 - 信息不完整时主动询问\n- 👨‍👩‍👧‍👦 多用户支持 - 10种不同消费风格\n- 📝 历史记忆 - 记录用户偏好\n\n## 快速开始\n\n```bash\n# 启动服务\ncd workspace\nnode family-sync-server.js\n```\n\n服务将在 http://localhost:3847 启动\n\n## 飞书配置\n\n### 1. 创建 Agent\n\n在 OpenClaw 中创建 `intent-agent`，绑定飞书渠道。\n\n### 2. 配置用户\n\n在 `workspace/USER/` 目录下配置用户：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"userId\": \"your_id\",\n  \"family_name\": \"你家\",\n  \"members\": [\"爸爸\", \"妈妈\", \"孩子\"],\n  \"income_level\": \"中\",\n  \"consume_style\": \"理性\",\n  \"has_child\": true,\n  \"has_elderly\": false\n}\n```\n\n### 3. 飞书对话\n\n用户通过飞书发送消息，Agent 自动：\n- 识别消费意图\n- 加载对应用户配置\n- 返回识别结果或追问\n\n## API\n\n```bash\n# 测试\ncurl -X POST http://localhost:3847/api/chat \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"message\":\"给孩子买手机\",\"userId\":\"wuhaichao\"}'\n```\n\n## 用户配置\n\n| userId | 消费风格 | 手机预算 |\n|--------|----------|----------|\n| wuhaichao | 大方 | 5000-8000 |\n| lihua | 理性 | 2000-4000 |\n| zhangsan | 大方 | 5000-8000 |\n| wangmei | 节俭 | 1000-2000 |\n| liuxiao | 适度 | 3000-5000 |\n| chenyun | 理性 | 2000-4000 |\n| zhaolei | 大方 | 5000-8000 |\n| sunli | 节俭 | 1000-2000 |\n| yangfan | 奢侈 | 10000+ |\n| zhoujing | 理性 | 2000-4000 |\n\n## 文件结构\n\n```\nintent-agent/\n├── workspace/               # 工作目录\n│   ├── AGENTS.md         # 核心规则\n│   ├── USER/             # 用户配置\n│   └── memory/           # 用户记忆\n├── skills/               # 技能模块\n├── agent-config/         # 代理配置\n└── config/               # 配置文件\n```\n\n## 响应示例\n\n**完整识别：**\n```json\n{\n  \"intent\": {\n    \"target\": \"孩子\",\n    \"object\": \"手机\",\n    \"budget\": \"5000-8000\",\n    \"is_complete\": true\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**需要追问：**\n```json\n{\n  \"intent\": {\"is_complete\": false},\n  \"next_question\": \"想买什么商品？\"\n}\n```\n\n## License\n\nMIT\nEOF\n\necho \"README 已更新（包含飞书配置）\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":105315,"output":768,"cacheRead":9179,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":115262,"cost":{"input":0.0315945,"output":0.0009216,"cacheRead":0.00027537,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.032791469999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773393547468}}
