{"type":"message","id":"7f4de9e4","parentId":"a87ead81","timestamp":"2026-03-13T09:19:47.547Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我确认一下更新后的README","thinkingSignature":"6b5ba7a157a9a04948554b24d6d8f5fd119dfc1c4bb3bb7fa9d008d6ae7c87f4"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_zmwp77sc9dhj_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /home/robot/.openclaw/workspace-family_consumption_intent/git/intent-agent/README.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":106108,"output":53,"cacheRead":9179,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":115340,"cost":{"input":0.0318324,"output":0.0000636,"cacheRead":0.00027537,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.03217136999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773393584220}}
{"type":"message","id":"ff5c8590","parentId":"7f4de9e4","timestamp":"2026-03-13T09:19:47.554Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_zmwp77sc9dhj_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Intent Agent - 家庭消费意图识别助手\n\n智能识别家庭成员的消费意图，提供个性化选购建议。\n\n## 功能\n\n- 🎯 意图识别 - 识别消费对象(target)和商品(object)\n- 💰 预算预测 - 根据消费风格自动匹配预算\n- 💬 智能追问 - 信息不完整时主动询问\n- 👨👩👧👦 多用户支持 - 10种不同消费风格\n- 📝 历史记忆 - 记录用户偏好\n\n## 快速开始\n\n```bash\n# 启动服务\ncd workspace\nnode family-sync-server.js\n```\n\n服务将在 http://localhost:3847 启动\n\n## 飞书配置\n\n### 1. 创建 Agent\n\n在 OpenClaw 中创建 `intent-agent`，绑定飞书渠道。\n\n### 2. 配置用户\n\n在 `workspace/USER/` 目录下配置用户：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"userId\": \"your_id\",\n  \"family_name\": \"你家\",\n  \"members\": [\"爸爸\", \"妈妈\", \"孩子\"],\n  \"income_level\": \"中\",\n  \"consume_style\": \"理性\",\n  \"has_child\": true,\n  \"has_elderly\": false\n}\n```\n\n### 3. 飞书对话\n\n用户通过飞书发送消息，Agent 自动：\n- 识别消费意图\n- 加载对应用户配置\n- 返回识别结果或追问\n\n## API\n\n```bash\n# 测试\ncurl -X POST http://localhost:3847/api/chat \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"message\":\"给孩子买手机\",\"userId\":\"wuhaichao\"}'\n```\n\n## 用户配置\n\n| userId | 消费风格 | 手机预算 |\n|--------|----------|----------|\n| wuhaichao | 大方 | 5000-8000 |\n| lihua | 理性 | 2000-4000 |\n| zhangsan | 大方 | 5000-8000 |\n| wangmei | 节俭 | 1000-2000 |\n| liuxiao | 适度 | 3000-5000 |\n| chenyun | 理性 | 2000-4000 |\n| zhaolei | 大方 | 5000-8000 |\n| sunli | 节俭 | 1000-2000 |\n| yangfan | 奢侈 | 10000+ |\n| zhoujing | 理性 | 2000-4000 |\n\n## 文件结构\n\n```\nintent-agent/\n├── workspace/               # 工作目录\n│   ├── AGENTS.md         # 核心规则\n│   ├── USER/             # 用户配置\n│   └── memory/           # 用户记忆\n├── skills/               # 技能模块\n├── agent-config/         # 代理配置\n└── config/               # 配置文件\n```\n\n## 响应示例\n\n**完整识别：**\n```json\n{\n  \"intent\": {\n    \"target\": \"孩子\",\n    \"object\": \"手机\",\n    \"budget\": \"5000-8000\",\n    \"is_complete\": true\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**需要追问：**\n```json\n{\n  \"intent\": {\"is_complete\": false},\n  \"next_question\": \"想买什么商品？\"\n}\n```\n\n## License\n\nMIT"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":6,"aggregated":"# Intent Agent - 家庭消费意图识别助手\n\n智能识别家庭成员的消费意图，提供个性化选购建议。\n\n## 功能\n\n- 🎯 意图识别 - 识别消费对象(target)和商品(object)\n- 💰 预算预测 - 根据消费风格自动匹配预算\n- 💬 智能追问 - 信息不完整时主动询问\n- 👨👩👧👦 多用户支持 - 10种不同消费风格\n- 📝 历史记忆 - 记录用户偏好\n\n## 快速开始\n\n```bash\n# 启动服务\ncd workspace\nnode family-sync-server.js\n```\n\n服务将在 http://localhost:3847 启动\n\n## 飞书配置\n\n### 1. 创建 Agent\n\n在 OpenClaw 中创建 `intent-agent`，绑定飞书渠道。\n\n### 2. 配置用户\n\n在 `workspace/USER/` 目录下配置用户：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"userId\": \"your_id\",\n  \"family_name\": \"你家\",\n  \"members\": [\"爸爸\", \"妈妈\", \"孩子\"],\n  \"income_level\": \"中\",\n  \"consume_style\": \"理性\",\n  \"has_child\": true,\n  \"has_elderly\": false\n}\n```\n\n### 3. 飞书对话\n\n用户通过飞书发送消息，Agent 自动：\n- 识别消费意图\n- 加载对应用户配置\n- 返回识别结果或追问\n\n## API\n\n```bash\n# 测试\ncurl -X POST http://localhost:3847/api/chat \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"message\":\"给孩子买手机\",\"userId\":\"wuhaichao\"}'\n```\n\n## 用户配置\n\n| userId | 消费风格 | 手机预算 |\n|--------|----------|----------|\n| wuhaichao | 大方 | 5000-8000 |\n| lihua | 理性 | 2000-4000 |\n| zhangsan | 大方 | 5000-8000 |\n| wangmei | 节俭 | 1000-2000 |\n| liuxiao | 适度 | 3000-5000 |\n| chenyun | 理性 | 2000-4000 |\n| zhaolei | 大方 | 5000-8000 |\n| sunli | 节俭 | 1000-2000 |\n| yangfan | 奢侈 | 10000+ |\n| zhoujing | 理性 | 2000-4000 |\n\n## 文件结构\n\n```\nintent-agent/\n├── workspace/               # 工作目录\n│   ├── AGENTS.md         # 核心规则\n│   ├── USER/             # 用户配置\n│   └── memory/           # 用户记忆\n├── skills/               # 技能模块\n├── agent-config/         # 代理配置\n└── config/               # 配置文件\n```\n\n## 响应示例\n\n**完整识别：**\n```json\n{\n  \"intent\": {\n    \"target\": \"孩子\",\n    \"object\": \"手机\",\n    \"budget\": \"5000-8000\",\n    \"is_complete\": true\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**需要追问：**\n```json\n{\n  \"intent\": {\"is_complete\": false},\n  \"next_question\": \"想买什么商品？\"\n}\n```\n\n## License\n\nMIT","cwd":"/home/robot/.openclaw/workspace-family_consumption_intent"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773393587553}}
{"type":"message","id":"598d1dda","parentId":"ff5c8590","timestamp":"2026-03-13T09:19:51.278Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"README已经更新完成，包含了飞书配置说明。","thinkingSignature":"a6daab135600b709900a2eded601e26cbcb63ccdb2b49d1eef9db995bbd5099a"},{"type":"text","text":"已更新 README，包含飞书配置说明！\n\n**新增内容：**\n```\n## 飞书配置\n\n### 1. 创建 Agent\n在 OpenClaw 中创建 intent-agent，绑定飞书渠道\n\n### 2. 配置用户\n在 workspace/USER/ 目录下配置用户 JSON\n\n### 3. 飞书对话\n用户通过飞书发送消息，自动识别\n```"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":106856,"output":94,"cacheRead":9179,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":116129,"cost":{"input":0.032056799999999996,"output":0.00011279999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00027537,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.03244497}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773393587555}}
{"type":"message","id":"6f54fde9","parentId":"598d1dda","timestamp":"2026-03-13T09:21:01.193Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54092173f084b2902ea5bdeeac2\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_d0f1627a7a508d84d750914fbb6a2fc2\",\n  \"sender\": \"吴海超\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-03-13 17:21 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"吴海超 (ou_d0f1627a7a508d84d750914fbb6a2fc2)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_d0f1627a7a508d84d750914fbb6a2fc2\",\n  \"name\": \"吴海超\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b54092173f084b2902ea5bdeeac2]\n吴海超: 按照这种形式写readme   Quoter Agent\n报价助手 Agent，基于 OpenClaw 框架运行。\n简介\nQuoter 是一个专业的报价测算 Agent，负责处理销售报价、测算计算等需求。\n目录结构\n```PLAIN_TEXT\nquoter-agent/\n├── workspace/          # Agent 工作目录\n│   ├── IDENTITY.md    # Agent 身份定义\n│   ├── USER.md        # 用户信息\n│   ├── SOUL.md        # Agent 风格设定\n│   └── ...\n├── skills/\n│   └── quote/\n│       └── SKILL.md   # 报价测算技能规范\n├── agent-config/\n│   └── quoter/\n│       ├── agent/     # 模型配置\n│       └── sessions/ # 会话存储\n└── config/\n    └── quoter.json   # OpenClaw 配置片段\n```\n快速开始\n1. 安装 DingTalk 插件\n\\# 安装 DingTalk 插件（推荐）\nopenclaw plugins install @soimy/dingtalk\n重启 Gateway 使插件生效：\nopenclaw gateway restart\n2. 配置插件白名单\n在 \\~/.openclaw/openclaw.json 中添加：\n\\{\n  \"plugins\": \\{\n    \"enabled\": true,\n    \"allow\": \\[\"dingtalk\"\\]\n  \\}\n\\}\n3. 安装 OpenClaw\n参考官方文档安装 OpenClaw：[https://docs.openclaw.ai](https://docs.openclaw.ai/)\n2. 配置 Agent\n方式一：整合到现有 OpenClaw\n将 config/quoter.json 中的配置合并到 \\~/.openclaw/openclaw.json：\n\\{\n  \"agents\": \\{\n    \"list\": \\[\n      // 添加 agent 配置\n      \\{\n        \"id\": \"quoter\",\n        \"name\": \"Quoter\",\n        \"workspace\": \"\\~/.openclaw/workspace\\-quoter\",\n        \"agentDir\": \"\\~/.openclaw/agents/quoter/agent\"\n      \\}\n    \\]\n  \\},\n  \"bindings\": \\[\n    \\{ \"match\": \\{ \"channel\": \"dingtalk\", \"accountId\": \"bot\\-quoter\" \\}, \"agentId\": \"quoter\" \\}\n  \\]\n\\}\n2.1 复制工作目录\ncp \\-r workspace/ \\~/.openclaw/workspace\\-quoter/\n2.2 复制 Agent 配置\ncp \\-r agent\\-config/quoter/ \\~/.openclaw/agents/quoter/\n2.3 复制技能（可选）\ncp \\-r skills/quote/ \\~/.openclaw/skills/\n3. 配置 DingTalk 机器人\n在钉钉开发者后台创建企业内部应用，配置 Stream 模式，然后在 openclaw.json 中添加：\n\\{\n  \"channels\": \\{\n    \"dingtalk\": \\{\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"accounts\": \\{\n        \"bot\\-quoter\": \\{\n          \"enabled\": true,\n          \"clientId\": \"your\\-client\\-id\",\n          \"clientSecret\": \"your\\-client\\-secret\",\n          \"robotCode\": \"your\\-robot\\-code\",\n          \"dmPolicy\": \"open\",\n          \"groupPolicy\": \"open\"\n        \\}\n      \\}\n    \\}\n  \\}\n\\}\n4. 重启 Gateway\nopenclaw gateway restart\n技能说明\n报价测算 \\(quote\\)\n触发条件：用户发送\"测算\"、\"报价\"、\"销售\"等需求\n处理流程：\n1. 需求理解 \\- 获取客户名称、产品类型、产品明细\n2. 读取模版 \\- 读取测算 Excel 模版\n3. 数据验证 \\- 验证产品名称、单价、数量\n4. 动态调整 \\- 根据实际销售产品调整模版\n5. 计算生成 \\- 计算毛利、生成 Excel\n6. 完整性检查 \\- 验证所有字段\n7. 返回结果 \\- 输出测算结果\n配置说明\nworkspace/ 目录\n\\- [IDENTITY.md](IDENTITY.md) \\- Agent 身份名称\n\\- [USER.md](USER.md) \\- 用户偏好设置\n\\- [SOUL.md](SOUL.md) \\- Agent 性格风格\n\\- [AGENTS.md](AGENTS.md) \\- 工作区规范\nagent\\-config/ 目录\n\\- agent/models.json \\- 模型配置\n\\- sessions/ \\- 会话历史存储\nconfig/ 目录\n\\- quoter.json \\- OpenClaw 配置片段（需合并到主配置）\n依赖\n\\- OpenClaw \\>= 2026.3.7\n\\- Node.js \\>= 22\n\\- DingTalk 机器人（Stream 模式）\n许可证\nMIT"}],"timestamp":1773393661191}}
{"type":"message","id":"9bbf45e5","parentId":"6f54fde9","timestamp":"2026-03-13T09:21:26.506Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to rewrite the README in the same format as the Quoter Agent example. Let me create a similar structure.","thinkingSignature":"6a6c533bc4c17ec1915743e80be1ec4fb325ad0e09269ef26362c0546ede2ff8"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_fznfixkjvz87_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat > /home/robot/.openclaw/workspace-family_consumption_intent/git/intent-agent/README.md << 'EOF'\n# Intent Agent\n\n家庭消费意图识别 Agent，基于 OpenClaw 框架运行。\n\n## 简介\n\nIntent Agent 是一个专业的家庭消费意图识别助手，负责识别家庭成员的消费意图、提供预算预测和选购建议。\n\n## 目录结构\n\n```\nintent-agent/\n├── workspace/          # Agent 工作目录\n│   ├── IDENTITY.md    # Agent 身份定义\n│   ├── USER.md        # 用户信息\n│   ├── SOUL.md        # Agent 风格设定\n│   ├── AGENTS.md      # 工作区规范\n│   ├── USER/          # 用户配置\n│   └── memory/        # 用户记忆\n├── skills/\n│   └── family-intent/\n│       └── SKILL.md   # 意图识别技能规范\n├── agent-config/\n│   └── intent-agent/\n│       ├── agent/     # 模型配置\n│       └── sessions/ # 会话存储\n└── config/\n    └── intent-agent.json   # OpenClaw 配置片段\n```\n\n## 快速开始\n\n### 1. 安装飞书插件\n\n```bash\n# 安装飞书插件（推荐）\nopenclaw plugins install feishu\n\n# 重启 Gateway 使插件生效\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n### 2. 配置插件白名单\n\n在 `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json` 中添加：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"plugins\": {\n    \"enabled\": true,\n    \"allow\": [\"feishu\"]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 3. 安装 OpenClaw\n\n参考官方文档安装 OpenClaw：https://docs.openclaw.ai\n\n### 4. 配置 Agent\n\n#### 方式一：整合到现有 OpenClaw\n\n将 `config/intent-agent.json` 中的配置合并到 `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json`：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"list\": [\n      {\n        \"id\": \"intent-agent\",\n        \"name\": \"Intent\",\n        \"workspace\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace-intent\",\n        \"agentDir\": \"~/.openclaw/agents/intent-agent/agent\"\n      }\n    ]\n  },\n  \"bindings\": [\n    { \"match\": { \"channel\": \"feishu\", \"accountId\": \"default\" }, \"agentId\": \"intent-agent\" }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n#### 4.1 复制工作目录\n\n```bash\ncp -r workspace/ ~/.openclaw/workspace-intent/\n```\n\n#### 4.2 复制 Agent 配置\n\n```bash\ncp -r agent-config/intent-agent/ ~/.openclaw/agents/\n```\n\n#### 4.3 复制技能（可选）\n\n```bash\ncp -r skills/family-intent/ ~/.openclaw/skills/\n```\n\n### 5. 配置飞书机器人\n\n在飞书开发者后台创建企业自建应用，配置机器人，然后在 openclaw.json 中添加：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"channels\": {\n    \"feishu\": {\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"accounts\": {\n        \"default\": {\n          \"enabled\": true,\n          \"appId\": \"your-app-id\",\n          \"appSecret\": \"your-app-secret\"\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 6. 重启 Gateway\n\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n## 功能说明\n\n### 意图识别 (family-intent)\n\n**触发条件**：用户发送消费相关需求\n\n**处理流程**：\n\n1. 意图理解 - 识别消费对象(target)和商品(object)\n2. 用户匹配 - 根据飞书用户ID加载对应配置\n3. 预算预测 - 根据消费风格自动匹配预算\n4. 智能追问 - 信息不完整时主动询问\n5. 返回结果 - 输出识别结果或追问问题\n\n## 配置说明\n\n### workspace/ 目录\n\n- [IDENTITY.md](workspace/IDENTITY.md) - Agent 身份名称\n- [USER.md](workspace/USER.md) - 用户偏好设置\n- [SOUL.md](workspace/SOUL.md) - Agent 性格风格\n- [AGENTS.md](workspace/AGENTS.md) - 工作区规范\n- [USER/](workspace/USER/) - 用户配置目录\n\n### agent-config/ 目录\n\n- agent/models.json - 模型配置\n- sessions/ - 会话历史存储\n\n### config/ 目录\n\n- intent-agent.json - OpenClaw 配置片段（需合并到主配置）\n\n## 用户配置\n\n在 `workspace/USER/` 目录下创建 `USER_{userId}.md` 文件：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"userId\": \"your_id\",\n  \"family_name\": \"你家\",\n  \"members\": [\"爸爸\", \"妈妈\", \"孩子\"],\n  \"income_level\": \"中\",\n  \"consume_style\": \"理性\",\n  \"has_child\": true,\n  \"has_elderly\": false\n}\n```\n\n## 预算预测规则\n\n| 消费风格 | 数码 | 家电 | 教育 | 服饰 |\n|----------|------|------|------|------|\n| 节俭 | 1000-2000 | 2000-3000 | 50-100 | 100-300 |\n| 适度 | 3000-5000 | 4000-6000 | 200-500 | 500-1000 |\n| 理性 | 2000-4000 | 3000-5000 | 100-300 | 300-500 |\n| 大方 | 5000-8000 | 6000-10000 | 500-1000 | 1000-2000 |\n| 奢侈 | 10000+ | 10000+ | 1000-3000 | 2000-5000 |\n\n## API\n\n```bash\n# 测试\ncurl -X POST http://localhost:3847/api/chat \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"message\":\"给孩子买手机\",\"userId\":\"wuhaichao\"}'\n```\n\n## 依赖\n\n- OpenClaw >= 2026.3.7\n- Node.js >= 22\n- 飞书机器人（企业自建应用）\n\n## 许可证\n\nMIT\nEOF\n\necho \"README 已更新\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":20,"output":1349,"cacheRead":107113,"cacheWrite":10060,"totalTokens":118542,"cost":{"input":0.000006,"output":0.0016187999999999999,"cacheRead":0.0032133899999999996,"cacheWrite":0.0012071999999999999,"total":0.0060453899999999994}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773393661192}}
