{"type":"message","id":"1c78c422","parentId":"22cd8dd2","timestamp":"2026-03-13T09:21:29.372Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me show the user the updated README.","thinkingSignature":"310153f03c568d4b171d30264d171b87a280ce2efb081ae248feb199b4c741dc"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_nnc6k7j6mjgj_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"head -80 /home/robot/.openclaw/workspace-family_consumption_intent/git/intent-agent/README.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":109382,"output":57,"cacheRead":9179,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":118618,"cost":{"input":0.0328146,"output":0.0000684,"cacheRead":0.00027537,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.03315837}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773393686515}}
{"type":"message","id":"253e4a36","parentId":"1c78c422","timestamp":"2026-03-13T09:21:29.380Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_nnc6k7j6mjgj_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Intent Agent\n\n家庭消费意图识别 Agent，基于 OpenClaw 框架运行。\n\n## 简介\n\nIntent Agent 是一个专业的家庭消费意图识别助手，负责识别家庭成员的消费意图、提供预算预测和选购建议。\n\n## 目录结构\n\n```\nintent-agent/\n├── workspace/          # Agent 工作目录\n│   ├── IDENTITY.md    # Agent 身份定义\n│   ├── USER.md        # 用户信息\n│   ├── SOUL.md        # Agent 风格设定\n│   ├── AGENTS.md      # 工作区规范\n│   ├── USER/          # 用户配置\n│   └── memory/        # 用户记忆\n├── skills/\n│   └── family-intent/\n│       └── SKILL.md   # 意图识别技能规范\n├── agent-config/\n│   └── intent-agent/\n│       ├── agent/     # 模型配置\n│       └── sessions/ # 会话存储\n└── config/\n    └── intent-agent.json   # OpenClaw 配置片段\n```\n\n## 快速开始\n\n### 1. 安装飞书插件\n\n```bash\n# 安装飞书插件（推荐）\nopenclaw plugins install feishu\n\n# 重启 Gateway 使插件生效\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n### 2. 配置插件白名单\n\n在 `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json` 中添加：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"plugins\": {\n    \"enabled\": true,\n    \"allow\": [\"feishu\"]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 3. 安装 OpenClaw\n\n参考官方文档安装 OpenClaw：https://docs.openclaw.ai\n\n### 4. 配置 Agent\n\n#### 方式一：整合到现有 OpenClaw\n\n将 `config/intent-agent.json` 中的配置合并到 `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json`：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"list\": [\n      {\n        \"id\": \"intent-agent\",\n        \"name\": \"Intent\",\n        \"workspace\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace-intent\",\n        \"agentDir\": \"~/.openclaw/agents/intent-agent/agent\"\n      }\n    ]\n  },\n  \"bindings\": [\n    { \"match\": { \"channel\": \"feishu\", \"accountId\": \"default\" }, \"agentId\": \"intent-agent\" }\n  ]"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":6,"aggregated":"# Intent Agent\n\n家庭消费意图识别 Agent，基于 OpenClaw 框架运行。\n\n## 简介\n\nIntent Agent 是一个专业的家庭消费意图识别助手，负责识别家庭成员的消费意图、提供预算预测和选购建议。\n\n## 目录结构\n\n```\nintent-agent/\n├── workspace/          # Agent 工作目录\n│   ├── IDENTITY.md    # Agent 身份定义\n│   ├── USER.md        # 用户信息\n│   ├── SOUL.md        # Agent 风格设定\n│   ├── AGENTS.md      # 工作区规范\n│   ├── USER/          # 用户配置\n│   └── memory/        # 用户记忆\n├── skills/\n│   └── family-intent/\n│       └── SKILL.md   # 意图识别技能规范\n├── agent-config/\n│   └── intent-agent/\n│       ├── agent/     # 模型配置\n│       └── sessions/ # 会话存储\n└── config/\n    └── intent-agent.json   # OpenClaw 配置片段\n```\n\n## 快速开始\n\n### 1. 安装飞书插件\n\n```bash\n# 安装飞书插件（推荐）\nopenclaw plugins install feishu\n\n# 重启 Gateway 使插件生效\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n### 2. 配置插件白名单\n\n在 `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json` 中添加：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"plugins\": {\n    \"enabled\": true,\n    \"allow\": [\"feishu\"]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 3. 安装 OpenClaw\n\n参考官方文档安装 OpenClaw：https://docs.openclaw.ai\n\n### 4. 配置 Agent\n\n#### 方式一：整合到现有 OpenClaw\n\n将 `config/intent-agent.json` 中的配置合并到 `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json`：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"list\": [\n      {\n        \"id\": \"intent-agent\",\n        \"name\": \"Intent\",\n        \"workspace\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace-intent\",\n        \"agentDir\": \"~/.openclaw/agents/intent-agent/agent\"\n      }\n    ]\n  },\n  \"bindings\": [\n    { \"match\": { \"channel\": \"feishu\", \"accountId\": \"default\" }, \"agentId\": \"intent-agent\" }\n  ]","cwd":"/home/robot/.openclaw/workspace-family_consumption_intent"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773393689378}}
{"type":"message","id":"de3e5347","parentId":"253e4a36","timestamp":"2026-03-13T09:21:34.386Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The README is now updated in the same format as the Quoter Agent. Let me confirm to the user.","thinkingSignature":"8e2613172a19ddf81d415e91784f903a7245bba69836c724b7a4ad76d24d85cc"},{"type":"text","text":"已按照相同格式更新 README！\n\n```\nintent-agent/\n├── workspace/          # Agent 工作目录\n│   ├── IDENTITY.md    # Agent 身份定义\n│   ├── USER.md        # 用户信息\n│   ├── SOUL.md        # Agent 风格设定\n│   └── ...\n├── skills/\n│   └── family-intent/\n│       └── SKILL.md   # 技能规范\n├── agent-config/\n│   └── intent-agent/\n│       ├── agent/     # 模型配置\n│       └── sessions/ # 会话存储\n└── config/\n    └── intent-agent.json   # OpenClaw 配置\n```\n\n包含完整的飞书配置说明 👍"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":109920,"output":162,"cacheRead":9179,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":119261,"cost":{"input":0.032976,"output":0.00019439999999999998,"cacheRead":0.00027537,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.03344576999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773393689380}}
