{"type":"message","id":"e8469c1a","parentId":"32ad1a32","timestamp":"2026-03-13T09:27:01.228Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想知道如何获取GitHub的SSH key或Personal Access Token，让我能够推送代码到GitHub。\n\n通常有几种方式：\n1. SSH Key - 需要在GitHub账号中添加SSH公钥\n2. Personal Access Token (PAT) - 需要生成并配置\n\n让我给用户说明。","thinkingSignature":"42add98e89930b455180924461cc1e337dd4551ea73b6c8393675782eea682a0"},{"type":"text","text":"有两种方式可以让我推送代码到 GitHub：\n\n## 方式1：SSH Key（推荐）\n\n```bash\n# 1. 生成 SSH Key（如果还没有）\nssh-keygen -t ed25519 -C \"robot@openclaw.ai\"\n\n# 2. 查看公钥\ncat ~/.ssh/id_ed25519.pub\n```\n\n然后在 GitHub 添加：\n- 进入 GitHub → Settings → SSH and GPG keys → New SSH key\n- 粘贴公钥\n\n## 方式2：Personal Access Token\n\n```bash\n# 1. 在 GitHub 生成 Token\n# Settings → Developer settings → Personal access tokens → Tokens (classic)\n# 生成新 Token，勾选 repo 权限\n\n# 2. 配置 git\ngit remote add origin https://你的用户名:TOKEN@github.com/ennwork2026/hcm-huild-tools.git\n```\n\n---\n\n**现在我这里没有配置 GitHub 认证**，你需要：\n\n1. 在你的 GitHub 账号上添加 SSH 公钥（或生成 Token）\n2. 或者你手动下载 zip 包上传：\n\n```\n/home/robot/.openclaw/workspace-family_consumption_intent/git/intent-agent.zip\n```\n\n你想用哪种方式？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":20,"output":310,"cacheRead":9179,"cacheWrite":110225,"totalTokens":119734,"cost":{"input":0.000006,"output":0.000372,"cacheRead":0.00027537,"cacheWrite":0.013227,"total":0.01388037}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773393986497}}
