{"type":"message","id":"ead80482","parentId":"fd70cda4","timestamp":"2026-03-13T10:02:54.393Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问 family-sync-server.js 是干什么用的。","thinkingSignature":"0637a041ddee09b0095d0b59c52b5fd2e33972e8abdf3f85933e955e5348b538"},{"type":"text","text":"`family-sync-server.js` 是 **意图识别 API 服务**。\n\n**功能：**\n- 接收用户消息\n- 识别消费意图（target + object）\n- 追问缺失信息\n- 返回识别结果和推荐建议\n\n**运行方式：**\n```bash\nnode family-sync-server.js\n# 启动服务在 http://localhost:3847\n```\n\n**API 调用：**\n```bash\ncurl -X POST http://localhost:3847/api/chat \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"message\":\"给孩子买手机\",\"userId\":\"wuhaichao\"}'\n```\n\n这是整个 Agent 的核心后端服务 👍"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":20,"output":151,"cacheRead":163437,"cacheWrite":849,"totalTokens":164457,"cost":{"input":0.000006,"output":0.00018119999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00490311,"cacheWrite":0.00010188,"total":0.00519219}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773396168259}}
